name="0687b08" id="0687b08"></a><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><a 
name="0687b09" id="0687b09"></a><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><a 
name="0687b10" id="0687b10"></a>有因法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><a 
name="0687b11" id="0687b11"></a>涅盤此初世道能引出世出世聖道名有因法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0687b12" id="0687b12"></a>只出世法至有因法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二引涅盤涅盤有彼出<a 
name="0687b13" id="0687b13"></a>世聖道能引發因名有因法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由如是等至有因<a 
name="0687b14" id="0687b14"></a>諸法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二&#x63D4;結釋理實十因所起之果對能起<a 
name="0688a01" id="0688a01"></a>因皆有因法今示方隅且舉三因所起果法名有因<a 
name="0688a02" id="0688a02"></a>法餘非無也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次此中至名有果法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0688a03" id="0688a03"></a>明有果法文分為二先釋後結釋中有五一有等流<a 
name="0688a04" id="0688a04"></a>果二有異熟果三有增上果四有士用果五有離繫<a 
name="0688a05" id="0688a05"></a>果此前二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若有三處至名有果法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三<a 
name="0688a06" id="0688a06"></a>有增上果文分為二先釋後結釋中有七第七等中<a 
name="0688a07" id="0688a07"></a>二種三者謂善不善二中各有反教思三餘可悉也。</p><a 
name="0688a08" id="0688a08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若現法中至有果法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四有士用果文具釋<a 
name="0688a09" id="0688a09"></a>結釋中有二文易可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若趣世間至二道差別。</p><a 
name="0688a10" id="0688a10"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五有離繫果文分三分初各別釋次重料揀後<a 
name="0688a11" id="0688a11"></a>&#x63D4;結之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由如是等至若離繫果。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後&#x63D4;結<a 
name="0688a12" id="0688a12"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論與<span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span>非有果法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二無因果法<a 
name="0688a13" id="0688a13"></a>反上應知<span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span><span title="未知的文字">▆</span>生至廣分別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十六緣<a 
name="0688a14" id="0688a14"></a>起諸法門前<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>廣明故不重也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略由至果<a 
name="0688b01" id="0688b01"></a>故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十七內法差別門文分為二一依實立二<a 
name="0688b02" id="0688b02"></a>依假立初文有四一摽二徵三列四釋此前三也。</p><a 
name="0688b03" id="0688b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若於是處至名內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋之中文分為五<a 
name="0688b04" id="0688b04"></a>一辯假名二彰妄執三明增上四明攝受五明事故<a 
name="0688b05" id="0688b05"></a>此初分二先釋後結釋中所言於是處者內蘊處也<a 
name="0688b06" id="0688b06"></a>謂於內蘊假立我等名內法處。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若於是處至名<a 
name="0688b07" id="0688b07"></a>內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰妄執此依多分而計即蘊妄起執<a 
name="0688b08" id="0688b08"></a>說理實亦計離蘊之法以為我也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若由此法至<a 
name="0688b09" id="0688b09"></a>名內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明增上由此六根為增上故色等<a 
name="0688b10" id="0688b10"></a>外處差別而生為所受用說能受者名為內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0688b11" id="0688b11"></a>若能攝受至名內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明攝受謂阿賴耶能<a 
name="0688b12" id="0688b12"></a>攝受彼三性種子悉在識中故名內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若五種<a 
name="0688b13" id="0688b13"></a>清淨至名內法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五明事故根心體事而是內<a 
name="0688b14" id="0688b14"></a>法故名為內。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又有假名至名內故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二依<a 
name="0689a01" id="0689a01"></a>假立立餘法者心所有法及扶根塵無表色等若對<a 
name="0689a02" id="0689a02"></a>能緣根境分之合名為外為由依內而可得故故雖<a 
name="0689a03" id="0689a03"></a>外處假亦名內。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次應知至名為色。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十<a 
name="0689a04" id="0689a04"></a>八名色所攝門文分為二先色後名色中有二謂釋<a 
name="0689a05" id="0689a05"></a>及結釋中有二一依增長二明變壞故以二義而立<a 
name="0689a06" id="0689a06"></a>色名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論其餘四蘊至說之為名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯其名<a 
name="0689a07" id="0689a07"></a>文分為二先釋後結釋中有二謂於諸法施設種種<a 
name="0689a08" id="0689a08"></a>名言勢力為所依故四蘊尋名緣於所緣有所歸趣<a 
name="0689a09" id="0689a09"></a>故從所依言說之名能依四蘊故名名也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次<a 
name="0689a10" id="0689a10"></a>略由至法差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十九執非執受門文分為二<a 
name="0689a11" id="0689a11"></a>先明執受後非執受初中有四一標二徵三釋四結<a 
name="0689a12" id="0689a12"></a>此初標也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論何等為五至非執受故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二徵<a 
name="0689a13" id="0689a13"></a>三釋釋中有五一辯色執受二明內執受三任持執<a 
name="0689a14" id="0689a14"></a>受四變異執受五<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>益執受此初先明唯色執受揀<a 
name="0689b01" id="0689b01"></a>心非色而不緣之以所緣心相無用故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又於色<a 
name="0689b02" id="0689b02"></a>中至執受故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明內執受揀外五塵識雖緣<a 
name="0689b03" id="0689b03"></a>之而不執受外塵不能生覺受故根依屬者內扶塵<a 
name="0689b04" id="0689b04"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又心心法至非執受故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三任持執受<a 
name="0689b05" id="0689b05"></a>揀扶塵等不能持心故非執受。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又執受色至故<a 
name="0689b06" id="0689b06"></a>名執受。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四變異執受文分為四一標二徵三<a 
name="0689b07" id="0689b07"></a>列四釋此標也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論何等為四至所緣境故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0689b08" id="0689b08"></a>二徵三列。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂由外色至喜樂攝受。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋<a 
name="0689b09" id="0689b09"></a>分四一外色逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>二內界順違三煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>所纏四所緣<a 
name="0689b10" id="0689b10"></a>審慮由此四故故內根身領此順違生<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>益等名為<a 
name="0689b11" id="0689b11"></a>執受如習定者作水觀時外觸違順定境持緣後出<a 
name="0689b12" id="0689b12"></a>之時方生<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>益識若不緣彼後<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>益憑何以生是故<a 
name="0689b13" id="0689b13"></a>本識依根受<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>後時意識方起解心故說色根名執<a 
name="0689b14" id="0689b14"></a>受色由外觸故便變異生餘可知也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又為<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>害<a 
name="0690a01" id="0690a01"></a>至名變異。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>益執受義思可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是<a 
name="0690a02" id="0690a02"></a>若色至諸法差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四&#x63D4;結釋若如是緣結前<a 
name="0690a03" id="0690a03"></a>第四令成變異結第五也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論與此相違至執受法。</p><a 
name="0690a04" id="0690a04"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後非執受非執受等如五十三亦具明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0690a05" id="0690a05"></a>復次至名有色法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二十明有色法門文分為<a 
name="0690a06" id="0690a06"></a>二一辯體相二結止餘初中有二先&#x63D4;出體後彰差<a 
name="0690a07" id="0690a07"></a>別此初出體謂四大種及所造中十一種色變礙現<a 
name="0690a08" id="0690a08"></a>生名有色體。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問如四大種至大種所造。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0690a09" id="0690a09"></a>後彰差別有三問荅文即為三初問荅中文復為二<a 
name="0690a10" id="0690a10"></a>一辯色造因二明作業事初中有二一明造所因二<a 
name="0690a11" id="0690a11"></a>辯種方所初中又二先問後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至大<a 
name="0690a12" id="0690a12"></a>種所造。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅意云雖能所造各有自種以所<a 
name="0690a13" id="0690a13"></a>造色隨能造種故說所造由能造造言根心中有種<a 
name="0690b01" id="0690b01"></a>子者根中有種唯隨轉理心中有種通於隨轉及正理<a 
name="0690b02" id="0690b02"></a>說正理賴耶正持種故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論隨逐色根至名無方所。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0690b03" id="0690b03"></a>曰二辯種方所然種體相實無方所隨彼所依明有無<a 
name="0690b04" id="0690b04"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又諸大種至所生大種。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰作業事文分<a 
name="0690b05" id="0690b05"></a>三分一明界作業二辯不相離三明業具闕此初復三<a 
name="0690b06" id="0690b06"></a>謂摽列釋釋中有二界者種也作業現也謂現四大<a 
name="0690b07" id="0690b07"></a>如次而有能持能攝能熟能長之作業也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又諸大<a 
name="0690b08" id="0690b08"></a>種至尼等聚。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯不相離文別有二先摽後釋<a 
name="0690b09" id="0690b09"></a>釋中又二謂法及喻喻復有二是及非也因所成者如<a 
name="0690b10" id="0690b10"></a>五十四。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又於一向至方能作業。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明業具闕文<a 
name="0690b11" id="0690b11"></a>分為二先&#x60E3;料揀後別分別&#x60E3;中有二一明堅聚二例<a 
name="0690b12" id="0690b12"></a>水等此初又二一彰業用二無業用初中復二一明堅聚<a 
name="0690b13" id="0690b13"></a>唯有地相二約欲色顯境有無初堅聚中一向堅者乾<a 
name="0691a01" id="0691a01"></a>土石等名一向堅餘水等中唯有種者於乾聚中唯有<a 
name="0691a02" id="0691a02"></a>水等濕之種性未起現行故唯種也又唯言聲不論觸<a 
name="0691a03" id="0691a03"></a>者以所造觸離能造無故隨地等彰有及無而不言也。</p><a 
name="0691a04" id="0691a04"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是至次第亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二例水等准堅應知故不<a 
name="0691a05" id="0691a05"></a>說也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論內色聚中至融消即流。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別分別文<a 
name="0691a06" id="0691a06"></a>分為二先內後外外具法喻內言具者<span class="gaiji">筋<!--gaiji,筋,1[筋-月+角],2&#x4225;,3--></span>骨名地血<a 
name="0691a07" id="0691a07"></a>名為水熱名為火動名為風欲有情身四必具故所<a 
name="0691a08" id="0691a08"></a>造具有其相易知外聚闕具理亦可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次至皆<a 
name="0691a09" id="0691a09"></a>是假有。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二問荅文分為二一<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>論前明二依<a 
name="0691a10" id="0691a10"></a>經問荅此初也准此論明&#x6F81;滑等法但依四大分位<a 
name="0691a11" id="0691a11"></a>假立隨大種者隨四大增立&#x6F81;滑等如前明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0691a12" id="0691a12"></a>問如世尊言至何密意耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二依經問荅文分為<a 
name="0691a13" id="0691a13"></a>二先問後荅此初問云准前論明&#x6F81;等是假離能造無<a 
name="0691a14" id="0691a14"></a>若准其理有體之法可須造之無法體無不可言造世<a 
name="0691b01" id="0691b01"></a>尊何意&#x6F81;等無法乃置造言根等有法而不言造故先<a 
name="0691b02" id="0691b02"></a>舉論後牒於經對為問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至大種所造。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0691b03" id="0691b03"></a>後荅文四一摽二列三釋四會釋中有二一自類假法<a 
name="0691b04" id="0691b04"></a>二異類實法假實雖異皆因大生並名所造能所俱<a 
name="0691b05" id="0691b05"></a>觸名為自類能所處異名為異類經依自類故不說<a 
name="0691b06" id="0691b06"></a>餘非餘根塵不名所造。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問世尊說有至大種所<a 
name="0691b07" id="0691b07"></a>造。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第三問荅文分為二先問後荅此先問云法<a 
name="0691b08" id="0691b08"></a>處定色何處大種而造起耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至大種所造。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0691b09" id="0691b09"></a>曰後荅意云定心所起影像定色隨彼所思何界之<a 
name="0691b10" id="0691b10"></a>中本質大種而能造也問如前論說定自在色隨何定<a 
name="0691b11" id="0691b11"></a>心即彼定地四大所造又五十四云此影像色從定心起<a 
name="0691b12" id="0691b12"></a>非四大造今此復云隨彼所緣本質之色四大種造各<a 
name="0691b13" id="0691b13"></a>有何意致斯不同荅古有釋云非大種造是盡理言定<a 
name="0692a01" id="0692a01"></a>所生色從心所起非對礙法故非大造今言從彼所緣<a 
name="0692a02" id="0692a02"></a>本質大種造者約遠緣說由觀彼質影像生故前說<a 
name="0692a03" id="0692a03"></a>自地大造造者從近緣說當地四大與影像色同時同<a 
name="0692a04" id="0692a04"></a>處故義說造理實不造有義定色雖非從彼業色大<a 
name="0692a05" id="0692a05"></a>造然從定色大種所生名定大造如變為魚魚身豈無<a 
name="0692a06" id="0692a06"></a>堅濕燸等故五十四云由彼定故生起大種然後造色<a 
name="0692a07" id="0692a07"></a>變異而生雖五十四前後文云影像之色從定心起非<a 
name="0692a08" id="0692a08"></a>大造者謂說假色假想變生云非所造非不從於近遠<a 
name="0692a09" id="0692a09"></a>四大為緣造起故諸定色皆從大造以為正說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於此<a 
name="0692a10" id="0692a10"></a>大種至不復現。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二結止餘。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何有法。</p><a 
name="0692a11" id="0692a11"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二十一有法差別門文分為二先問後荅此先問<a 
name="0692a12" id="0692a12"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂一切至說名有法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅荅中文分三分<a 
name="0692a13" id="0692a13"></a>初&#x60E3;出體次別徵釋後指廣文此初也一切世法三有<a 
name="0692a14" id="0692a14"></a>所攝名為有法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問阿羅漢等至名無漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次<a 
name="0692b01" id="0692b01"></a>別徵釋有二問荅此初復二先問後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅<a 
name="0692b02" id="0692b02"></a>至說名無漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問至此何密意。</p><a 
name="0692b03" id="0692b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二問荅文二准前此先問云前論所言一切世<a 
name="0692b04" id="0692b04"></a>法說名有法有法即是有漏法也云何世尊但說意<a 
name="0692b05" id="0692b05"></a>法及意識三名為有法餘不言之有何意趣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至<a 
name="0692b06" id="0692b06"></a>說如是言。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅意云因中意識意法等三有是應<a 
name="0692b07" id="0692b07"></a>斷有不應斷不應斷者是出世法應斷之者是世間法<a 
name="0692b08" id="0692b08"></a>為揀不斷故但說三名為有漏眼等五識根境等三因<a 
name="0692b09" id="0692b09"></a>位唯漏非通不斷故不言之非彼根心不名有漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此<a 
name="0692b10" id="0692b10"></a>中世尊至應知處。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後指廣文此不言也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次<a 
name="0692b11" id="0692b11"></a>云何有上法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二十二有無上法門文分為二先明有<a 
name="0692b12" id="0692b12"></a>上後明無上初中有二先徵後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂除涅槃<a 
name="0692b13" id="0692b13"></a>餘一切法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋之云有為法外更有無為勝上之<a 
name="0693a01" id="0693a01"></a>法名有上法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由五因緣至無上法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明無上<a 
name="0693a02" id="0693a02"></a>文中有四一摽二徵三釋四結謂此涅槃具五因緣體妙<a 
name="0693a03" id="0693a03"></a>殊勝更無過上名無上法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何應修法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0693a04" id="0693a04"></a>二十三修習有為門文分為二先徵後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0693a05" id="0693a05"></a>謂一切善有為法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二初&#x60E3;出體後彰差<a 
name="0693a06" id="0693a06"></a>別此初出體有漏無漏有為善法有所進修可名修<a 
name="0693a07" id="0693a07"></a>法無為不尒故以揀之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中應知至對治修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0693a08" id="0693a08"></a>曰後彰差別文分為二一別辯四修二攝之為二初中<a 
name="0693a09" id="0693a09"></a>有二先&#x60E3;標列後別解之此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中未生至名<a 
name="0693a10" id="0693a10"></a>得修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別解中文分為四一辯得修二辯習修<a 
name="0693a11" id="0693a11"></a>三除去修四對治修此得修也為得故修名曰得修<a 
name="0693a12" id="0693a12"></a>謂由修力得所未得諸善法故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>生善至名習<a 
name="0693a13" id="0693a13"></a>修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯習修習者慣也習即是修名曰習修<a 
name="0693a14" id="0693a14"></a>由此數習數修力故已生善法令得堅住不忘倍增名<a 
name="0693b01" id="0693b01"></a>習修也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>生不善至除去修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三除去修為除<a 
name="0693b02" id="0693b02"></a>故修名除去修由此修力除去現行諸不善故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論未<a 
name="0693b03" id="0693b03"></a>生不善至對治修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四對治修文分為二初&#x60E3;後<a 
name="0693b04" id="0693b04"></a>別此初也師子覺云修習對治名對治修對治未來<a 
name="0693b05" id="0693b05"></a>諸不善法令不生起名對治也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知此中至對治<a 
name="0693b06" id="0693b06"></a>修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別之中文分為四一猒對治二斷對治三<a 
name="0693b07" id="0693b07"></a>持對治四遠對治此初猒患對治修者即七作意中<a 
name="0693b08" id="0693b08"></a>了相勝解名猒對治謂觀蘊身有漏過患如瘡<span class="gaiji">癰<!--gaiji,癰,1[病-丙+(雍-〦)],2&#x3FC8;,3--></span>等<a 
name="0693b09" id="0693b09"></a>不生染著名對治也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論從遠離作意至斷對治修。</p><a 
name="0693b10" id="0693b10"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二斷對治即以遠離攝樂觀察方便究竟四種作<a 
name="0693b11" id="0693b11"></a>意名斷對治謂即方便及無間道能斷惑故名斷對<a 
name="0693b12" id="0693b12"></a>治。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論方便究竟至持對治修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三持對治以彼<a 
name="0693b13" id="0693b13"></a>第七為持對治謂解脫道任持斷得名持對治。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論從<a 
name="0694a01" id="0694a01"></a>此<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>上至遠分對治修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四遠對治即以後之勝<a 
name="0694a02" id="0694a02"></a>上地中七種作意望於前品所斷染法為遠對治謂<a 
name="0694a03" id="0694a03"></a>後諸道令先所斷煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>轉遠所以名為遠分治也。</p><a 
name="0694a04" id="0694a04"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此四種修至思惟修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二攝之為二文復分二先<a 
name="0694a05" id="0694a05"></a>&#x60E3;標列後別釋之此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中修身至受持修。</p><a 
name="0694a06" id="0694a06"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別釋中文分為二先明防護後辯思惟此初<a 
name="0694a07" id="0694a07"></a>也修身淨行名防護修防護根門令過不起即前習<a 
name="0694a08" id="0694a08"></a>修除去修也修戒謂即別脫律儀要從他受方自修<a 
name="0694a09" id="0694a09"></a>治名受持修體即前三一分修也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若靜慮地至為<a 
name="0694a10" id="0694a10"></a>修慧。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯思惟謂即定慧相應作意名作意<a 
name="0694a11" id="0694a11"></a>思惟修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何過去法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二十四三世法性<a 
name="0694a12" id="0694a12"></a>門文分三&#x53DA;初明過去次辯未來後彰現在初中有<a 
name="0694a13" id="0694a13"></a>二先徵後辯此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂因<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>受盡自性<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>滅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0694a14" id="0694a14"></a>曰後辯文二初明體別後明事別初中又二先釋後結<a 
name="0694b01" id="0694b01"></a>釋中又二一辯法無二明憶念初中有三一因二果三辯<a 
name="0694b02" id="0694b02"></a>為緣此前二也自性果也因果俱盡名為過去。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論無間<a 
name="0694b03" id="0694b03"></a>為緣為生餘法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三辯為緣文分為二初近後遠<a 
name="0694b04" id="0694b04"></a>近中又二先辯後遮此初也為生餘法故名過去若不<a 
name="0694b05" id="0694b05"></a>過去後法不生後得生者謂由過去法體已無彼方<a 
name="0694b06" id="0694b06"></a>生故故說為緣為生餘法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論除阿羅漢最後心法。</p><a 
name="0694b07" id="0694b07"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後遮後心非為後緣故揀之也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論熏習相續至<a 
name="0694b08" id="0694b08"></a>異熟當熟。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯遠緣名為過去過去現行雖<a 
name="0694b09" id="0694b09"></a>久<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>滅種能招果故說為緣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如所領受至諸作<a 
name="0694b10" id="0694b10"></a>月。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明憶念以辯差別謂有一類得宿命智<a 
name="0694b11" id="0694b11"></a>憶知本事名為過去或有一類不生宿智而不能知然<a 
name="0694b12" id="0694b12"></a>滅所顯無有作用亦名過去。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論是名過去諸法差別。</p><a 
name="0694b13" id="0694b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後結可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此過去法至所有盡滅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明<a 
name="0695a01" id="0695a01"></a>事別文分三段謂標徵釋釋中有五一<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span>那過去約<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span><a 
name="0695a02" id="0695a02"></a>那說二死沒過去約一期說三壞&#x5227;過去約壞&#x5227;說成<a 
name="0695a03" id="0695a03"></a>住等時未有滅壞不名過去四退失過去如習定者<a 
name="0695a04" id="0695a04"></a>先得後失名為過去五盡滅過去有餘依中惑業盡<a 
name="0695a05" id="0695a05"></a>滅無餘界中身智盡滅以盡滅故名為過去。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次<a 
name="0695a06" id="0695a06"></a>云何未來法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯未來文分為二先問後荅此<a 
name="0695a07" id="0695a07"></a>初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂因未受至遠當生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅文二一明<a 
name="0695a08" id="0695a08"></a>體別二明事別此初分三一因未受未受果也二自性未<a 
name="0695a09" id="0695a09"></a>受果體未生未酬因也三待緣生待緣生中而有&#x60E3;別<a 
name="0695a10" id="0695a10"></a>別有近遠。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論亦由五相至得未來。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明事別文分<a 
name="0695a11" id="0695a11"></a>為二先摽後列列中有五初二可知三成&#x5227;者未來<a 
name="0695a12" id="0695a12"></a>成&#x5227;現雖未至當可成故名曰未來四應現行五<a 
name="0695a13" id="0695a13"></a>應得法亦准此知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何現在法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明現<a 
name="0695a14" id="0695a14"></a>在文亦分二先徵後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂因已受用至清<a 
name="0695b01" id="0695b01"></a>淨所顯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二一明體別二明事別初文有<a 
name="0695b02" id="0695b02"></a>六一因用未盡二果用未盡三<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span>那即滅四&#x51B3;定壞<a 
name="0695b03" id="0695b03"></a>滅五雜染所顯六分淨所顯謂除無為無為非是<a 
name="0695b04" id="0695b04"></a>世所攝故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論亦由五相至心法等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明事別文<a 
name="0695b05" id="0695b05"></a>中有三謂標列釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何至欲界繫法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0695b06" id="0695b06"></a>二十五三界繫別門文分三&#x53DA;初明欲界次明色界後<a 
name="0695b07" id="0695b07"></a>無色界欲界文三謂徵釋結心不在定彰是散地若<a 
name="0695b08" id="0695b08"></a>得定時即非欲故生得等者異熟之心說為生得善<a 
name="0695b09" id="0695b09"></a>惡之意名為作意三世等法名<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>行等生及作意三世<a 
name="0695b10" id="0695b10"></a>法轉皆名欲界。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何至色界繫法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0695b11" id="0695b11"></a>次明色界文亦分三謂徵釋結釋中有二一明色定二<a 
name="0695b12" id="0695b12"></a>明生色此初也謂在欲界所得上定及定所起色界之<a 
name="0695b13" id="0695b13"></a>法皆色界繫問身在欲界亦得起上天眼耳通何故<a 
name="0696a01" id="0696a01"></a>但云意地諸法荅二通必由定意所引意所引故亦名<a 
name="0696a02" id="0696a02"></a>意地法由作意者顯起上地加行善心揀生得也。</p><a 
name="0696a03" id="0696a03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論或生色界至色界繫法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明生色所起之法<a 
name="0696a04" id="0696a04"></a>皆色所繫而言生得或作意者具起當地業報非報<a 
name="0696a05" id="0696a05"></a>二種心也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如色界繫至當知亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明無色<a 
name="0696a06" id="0696a06"></a>准色應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何善法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二十六三性法體<a 
name="0696a07" id="0696a07"></a>門文分為二一彰三體別二辯三相異初中有三一明善<a 
name="0696a08" id="0696a08"></a>性二明不善三明無記善中復二先徵後釋此初也。</p><a 
name="0696a09" id="0696a09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂若略說至名為安隱。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分四摽列徵釋<a 
name="0696a10" id="0696a10"></a>文顯可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論與此相違至不安隱。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明不善<a 
name="0696a11" id="0696a11"></a>返善應悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論無記諸法至非不安隱。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明無<a 
name="0696a12" id="0696a12"></a>記返前二性所有二因即是此性二因之義對法等<a 
name="0696a13" id="0696a13"></a>別應會異同。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又由五相至利他善行。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯三<a 
name="0696a14" id="0696a14"></a>相異文分為二先明善惡後明無記初中有二一明相<a 
name="0696b01" id="0696b01"></a>異二明強盛初中又二一明善性二明不善善中復二<a 
name="0696b02" id="0696b02"></a>先摽後釋釋中有五尋之可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又由五相至所顯<a 
name="0696b03" id="0696b03"></a>故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明不善&#x98DC;善知也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由五因緣至善法強<a 
name="0696b04" id="0696b04"></a>盛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明強盛文分為二初明善性後明不善善<a 
name="0696b05" id="0696b05"></a>中有四一摽二徵三列四釋釋中有五一明加行二明<a 
name="0696b06" id="0696b06"></a>宿習三攝勝德四田事處五明自性自性之中施戒<a 
name="0696b07" id="0696b07"></a>修三<span class="gaiji">[牙-(必-心)+?]<!--gaiji,,1[牙-(必-心)+?],2&#x3E26;,3--></span>有勝劣如文可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論與此相違至不善強<a 
name="0696b08" id="0696b08"></a>盛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明不善強盛五因對前善性&#x98DC;顯應悉。</p><a 
name="0696b09" id="0696b09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又由五相至色處聲處。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明無記文分為四一<a 
name="0696b10" id="0696b10"></a>摽二徵三列四釋釋中隨難偏明第五即顯長養<a 
name="0696b11" id="0696b11"></a>五根非情五塵扶根五塵並是自性無記所攝色聲二<a 
name="0696b12" id="0696b12"></a>處通善惡性所以除之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何學法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0696b13" id="0696b13"></a>十七三學法利門文分三分初明有學次明無學後<a 
name="0697a01" id="0697a01"></a>明非二初中有二先徵後辯此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂或預流至<a 
name="0697a02" id="0697a02"></a>慧學故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯分三謂標徵釋此中據勝及果<a 
name="0697a03" id="0697a03"></a>而說不云四向及資&#x7CAE;加行二人理實彼等所有進修<a 
name="0697a04" id="0697a04"></a>皆名學法對法第四而即取之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何無學至名<a 
name="0697a05" id="0697a05"></a>無學法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次明無學文具徵釋世出世善進修<a 
name="0697a06" id="0697a06"></a>滿足名為無學。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何非學至非無學法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0697a07" id="0697a07"></a>後明非二謂異生中所有三性無前二相故曰俱非。</p><a 
name="0697a08" id="0697a08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何見道所斷法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二十八三斷分別門<a 
name="0697a09" id="0697a09"></a>文分三分初明見斷次明修斷後明非斷見斷文二<a 
name="0697a10" id="0697a10"></a>先徵後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂薩迦耶至所斷法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0697a11" id="0697a11"></a>釋之中分別所起十種煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>及隨惑中分別起者皆<a 
name="0697a12" id="0697a12"></a>見所斷故言等也招惡趣業及彼所招難處之報并<a 
name="0697a13" id="0697a13"></a>女人身第八有等皆見所斷故置等言彼果等法由<a 
name="0697a14" id="0697a14"></a>因斷故亦得斷名非自性斷身邊二見斷通見修今<a 
name="0697b01" id="0697b01"></a>且明於見道斷者故云五見非全&#x60E3;取說為見斷。</p><a 
name="0697b02" id="0697b02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何修道至所斷法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次明修斷通其三性善<a 
name="0697b03" id="0697b03"></a>法無記名為斷者據離縛說其染法中除先所斷<a 
name="0697b04" id="0697b04"></a>分別染外餘之俱生六種染法名修所斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何非<a 
name="0697b05" id="0697b05"></a>所斷至非所斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明非斷此三斷義唯識第<a 
name="0697b06" id="0697b06"></a>六亦具明之應對同異。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何甚深難見法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0697b07" id="0697b07"></a>曰二十九甚深難見門文分為二先問後釋此初也。</p><a 
name="0697b08" id="0697b08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂一切法至甚深難見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分四一摽二徵<a 
name="0697b09" id="0697b09"></a>三釋四結甚深法二一第一甚深謂真如也二諸法<a 
name="0697b10" id="0697b10"></a>自性謂一切法此二言詮皆莫能迨故曰甚深然依<a 
name="0697b11" id="0697b11"></a>名言方乃舉了若不然者曷能了知法體差別起<a 
name="0697b12" id="0697b12"></a>修斷哉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是所說至思惟揀擇。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>結<a 
name="0697b13" id="0697b13"></a>勸思。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是諸法至更不復現。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰大文第二&#x60E3;<a 
name="0698a01" id="0698a01"></a>結止餘。</p><a 
name="0698a02" id="0698a02"></a><p style="margin-left: 2em"><span class="headname">論卷第六十七　攝&#x51B3;擇分中修所成慧地</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0698a03" id="0698a03"></a>如是<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>說至我今當說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰通行之中文分三分謂<a 
name="0698a04" id="0698a04"></a>聞思修聞思<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>明次彰修慧文分為二初結前生後<a 
name="0698a05" id="0698a05"></a>後依生正釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知略有至所成法修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0698a06" id="0698a06"></a>後依生正釋文分為二一別明修體二&#x60E3;結止餘初中<a 
name="0698a07" id="0698a07"></a>有三摽列及釋此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何聲聞至作意修。</p><a 
name="0698a08" id="0698a08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋依標文分十六一聲聞修文復分三一徵二<a 
name="0698a09" id="0698a09"></a>釋三&#x60E3;結之此初徵也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂如有一至聲聞法性。</p><a 
name="0698a10" id="0698a10"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二釋之中文分為五一彰種姓二明趣入三明住<a 
name="0698a11" id="0698a11"></a>行四明緣境五明修意此初舉人以彰法性。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論或<a 
name="0698a12" id="0698a12"></a>未證入至正性離生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明趣入謂發趣心前後<a 
name="0698a13" id="0698a13"></a>不同根性復異故於正性有證未證二不同也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論不<a 
name="0698a14" id="0698a14"></a>觀他利至利益事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明住行。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由安立諦至<a 
name="0698b01" id="0698b01"></a>法為境。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明緣境緣安立諦作意門者顯加<a 
name="0698b02" id="0698b02"></a>行位以觀安立四諦作意為方便門趣入真際內觀<a 
name="0698b03" id="0698b03"></a>如者此明緣真根本智位親以真如為所觀境緣有量<a 
name="0698b04" id="0698b04"></a>等而明緣俗後得智位緣有作四聖諦境故名有量<a 
name="0698b05" id="0698b05"></a>有量之法是分別心帶相而緣分別之法名分別法。</p><a 
name="0698b06" id="0698b06"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論為盡貪愛至修習作意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五明修意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論是名<a 
name="0698b07" id="0698b07"></a>聲聞至作意修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三&#x60E3;結之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何大乘相應作<a 
name="0698b08" id="0698b08"></a>意修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯大乘文分三分一徵二釋三&#x60E3;結之此<a 
name="0698b09" id="0698b09"></a>初徵也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂如有一至利益事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二釋之中文分<a 
name="0698b10" id="0698b10"></a>為五一明種姓二彰趣入三彰住行四明觀境五彰修<a 
name="0698b11" id="0698b11"></a>意此前三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由安立諦至法為境。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明觀<a 
name="0698b12" id="0698b12"></a>境加行根本後得三智所觀別也於初智中安非安<a 
name="0698b13" id="0698b13"></a>者別觀四諦名為安立觀二空理名非安立正智可<a 
name="0699a01" id="0699a01"></a>知後得通知真俗二境名緣無量離能所取&#x53F7;無分<a 
name="0699a02" id="0699a02"></a>別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論大悲增上至修習作意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五彰修意意為<a 
name="0699a03" id="0699a03"></a>自他二種修故文具摽釋尋之可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論是名大乘相應<a 
name="0699a04" id="0699a04"></a>作意修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三&#x60E3;結之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何影像修至影像修。</p><a 
name="0699a05" id="0699a05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三影像修文分三分謂徵釋結釋中有二先觀<a 
name="0699a06" id="0699a06"></a>後止慧性推求故云分別觀相應定名三摩地所觀<a 
name="0699a07" id="0699a07"></a>本質名所知事正觀作意所思影像是彼質類名為<a 
name="0699a08" id="0699a08"></a>同分止性證淨名無分別餘義同觀故顯揚云所行<a 
name="0699a09" id="0699a09"></a>本境法同分也故所知事為質明矣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何事邊際<a 
name="0699a10" id="0699a10"></a>至邊際修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四邊際修文分為二先徵後釋釋中<a 
name="0699a11" id="0699a11"></a>有二初修有為&#x60E3;有五句後修無為但思真如次盡所<a 
name="0699a12" id="0699a12"></a>有攝諸有為如所有者攝諸無為有無皆盡名為邊<a 
name="0699a13" id="0699a13"></a>際變影緣如亦名事也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何所作至成辦修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0699a14" id="0699a14"></a>曰五成辦修靜慮等法是所修作修作未滿不名成<a 
name="0699b01" id="0699b01"></a>辦<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>入根本故得辦名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何得修至名得修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0699b02" id="0699b02"></a>曰六辯得修文具徵釋釋中分三一示所修二明修相<a 
name="0699b03" id="0699b03"></a>三&#x60E3;結釋初中有二先約想明後兼餘德餘德無常<a 
name="0699b04" id="0699b04"></a>等想而有十種如本地分第二十明言自下地顯不修<a 
name="0699b05" id="0699b05"></a>上此據多分初修者說理實有下而亦修上故唯識云<a 
name="0699b06" id="0699b06"></a>前三無色有勝見道傍修得故言彼引等顯兼餘德<a 
name="0699b07" id="0699b07"></a>非唯前想亦因想等所引苦空無我等法皆令清淨<a 
name="0699b08" id="0699b08"></a>當生定地及能獲得自在成就名曰得修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何習<a 
name="0699b09" id="0699b09"></a>修至名習修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰七辯習修習謂倣習習即是修數<a 
name="0699b10" id="0699b10"></a>習前法名曰習修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何除去至自性諸相。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰八<a 
name="0699b11" id="0699b11"></a>除去修文分為二先徵後釋釋中有三初法次喻後<a 
name="0699b12" id="0699b12"></a>&#x60E3;結之喻中有二一想除顛倒喻二細除<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重喻此<a 
name="0699b13" id="0699b13"></a>初也定中影像諸相作意名為如楔是能出也自性<a 
name="0700a01" id="0700a01"></a>諸相是本質境猶如出楔是所出也影像相者謂作<a 
name="0700a02" id="0700a02"></a>無常不淨等相本質相者計身常樂我淨等相由觀<a 
name="0700a03" id="0700a03"></a>無常故除常倒假想不淨能除淨倒以能所除俱有<a 
name="0700a04" id="0700a04"></a>相故故喻於楔能所體同。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又如有一至除去修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0700a05" id="0700a05"></a>曰二細除<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重喻身有輕安名輕安身身有<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重名<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重<a 
name="0700a06" id="0700a06"></a>身以細除<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>故同楔也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何對治修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰九對治修<a 
name="0700a07" id="0700a07"></a>文分為二先徵後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂於猒患至對治修。</p><a 
name="0700a08" id="0700a08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二先列後釋此初列名而有四也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此<a 
name="0700a09" id="0700a09"></a>中猒患至所引作意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋之中有二復次此<a 
name="0700a10" id="0700a10"></a>初分四一明猒患二斷對治三持對治四遠對治此初<a 
name="0700a11" id="0700a11"></a>猒患謂世善道猒世過非名為猒患神通等行無記<a 
name="0700a12" id="0700a12"></a>無猒故以除之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論斷對治者至境作意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二斷<a 
name="0700a13" id="0700a13"></a>對治斷惑之心必緣如故故舉緣如彰斷作意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0700a14" id="0700a14"></a>持對治者至解脫道。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三持對治謂緣如後所有<a 
name="0700b01" id="0700b01"></a>後得及世出世無間道後所有解脫皆持對治咸能<a 
name="0700b02" id="0700b02"></a>持彼所斷德故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論遠分對治至上地之道。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四遠<a 
name="0700b03" id="0700b03"></a>對治由多修習有深防力令先所斷勢漸轉遠名遠<a 
name="0700b04" id="0700b04"></a>分對治。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復有差別至遠分對治。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二復次<a 
name="0700b05" id="0700b05"></a>文分為二先摽後釋釋中有四初二對治如次加行及<a 
name="0700b06" id="0700b06"></a>根本也第三持中轉依果者所證理也理是解脫智<a 
name="0700b07" id="0700b07"></a>之所持名持對治第四遠分後得智也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何少<a 
name="0700b08" id="0700b08"></a>分修至少分修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十少分修十想等中隨修於<a 
name="0700b09" id="0700b09"></a>一名為少分。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何遍行至遍行修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十一遍行<a 
name="0700b10" id="0700b10"></a>修所觀真境遍於一切能觀作意名遍行修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云<a 
name="0700b11" id="0700b11"></a>何動轉至動轉修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十二動轉修謂於無相修<a 
name="0700b12" id="0700b12"></a>方便時被諸有相之所動轉名動轉修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何有<a 
name="0700b13" id="0700b13"></a>加行至加行修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十三加行修無相修時未能任<a 
name="0701a01" id="0701a01"></a>運加功而作名加行修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何成辦至成辦修。</p><a 
name="0701a02" id="0701a02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十四成辦修涅槃菩提轉依<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>滿神通等至出<a 
name="0701a03" id="0701a03"></a>入自由名為成辦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何非修至成法修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十<a 
name="0701a04" id="0701a04"></a>五非修修謂散地諸善非由定成名非修成。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云<a 
name="0701a05" id="0701a05"></a>何修所成至成法修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十六修所成修所修之法<a 
name="0701a06" id="0701a06"></a>因定而得名修所修。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於此地中至不復現。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0701a07" id="0701a07"></a>二&#x60E3;結止餘然此修義名字體性數之增減諸門差<a 
name="0701a08" id="0701a08"></a>別如莊嚴論第十卷中顯揚十六對法第九及此論<a 
name="0701a09" id="0701a09"></a>中前三十四雖各明之今此義窮故不重現<a 
name="0701a10" id="0701a10"></a>攝&#x51B3;擇分中聲聞地。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>說至我今當說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第<a 
name="0701a11" id="0701a11"></a>二&#x51B3;擇瑜伽行中分之為二一明通行前<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>彰訖次明<a 
name="0701a12" id="0701a12"></a>別行文分為三初辯聲聞次明獨覺後彰菩薩初<a 
name="0701a13" id="0701a13"></a>中有三一結前生後二依生正釋三&#x60E3;結止餘此初也。</p><a 
name="0701a14" id="0701a14"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如本地分至般涅槃法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二依生正釋門分釋<a 
name="0701b01" id="0701b01"></a>四一彰性有無門二辯戒差別門三所知法異門四<span title="未知的文字">▆</span><a 
name="0701b02" id="0701b02"></a>等類別門初性門中子門分七一辯無種姓門二辯<a 
name="0701b03" id="0701b03"></a>有種姓門三具戒生福門四&#x5F83;他家法門五三處了知<a 
name="0701b04" id="0701b04"></a>門六所知名事門七辯緣四諦門初門分二先<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>摽舉<a 
name="0701b05" id="0701b05"></a>後釋外疑此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中或有至涅槃法耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0701b06" id="0701b06"></a>後釋疑中文分為五一釋無畢竟二辯無根難三彰<a 
name="0701b07" id="0701b07"></a>轉有姓四界具有無五辯生後姓初中有二先難後破<a 
name="0701b08" id="0701b08"></a>此初外人聞無疑起難。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論應誨彼言至不應道理。</p><a 
name="0701b09" id="0701b09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後破之中文分為二先徵後破破中又二一有性相<a 
name="0701b10" id="0701b10"></a>違破二無性違經破理思可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是誨已至無根有<a 
name="0701b11" id="0701b11"></a>情。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯無根難文分為二先難後破難中有二<a 
name="0701b12" id="0701b12"></a>初結前文後生正難難中有二先順後返其順難云雖<a 
name="0701b13" id="0701b13"></a>無無根而有情界得言種種雖無無姓有情之界何非<a 
name="0702a01" id="0702a01"></a>種種返難意云為成界異立無種姓應成界異立無<a 
name="0702a02" id="0702a02"></a>根情。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論應詰彼言至不應道理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後破之中文分<a 
name="0702a03" id="0702a03"></a>為二先徵後破破中有二一非情相例失二違宗所立失<a 
name="0702a04" id="0702a04"></a>所立失中若無根物非有情者難令立有無根有情<a 
name="0702a05" id="0702a05"></a>違自所許又我立情界有種種何得汝以無情為難<a 
name="0702a06" id="0702a06"></a>乘所立失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是詰<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>至般涅槃法耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰轉有<a 
name="0702a07" id="0702a07"></a>姓文分為二先難後破此先舉外類姓轉成難。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論應<a 
name="0702a08" id="0702a08"></a>詰彼言至不應道理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後破之中文分為二一喻<a 
name="0702a09" id="0702a09"></a>非相似失凡舉喻者與法類同今則不然故成非理<a 
name="0702a10" id="0702a10"></a>二無因非轉失若唯獨一無餘界者無因果生不應<a 
name="0702a11" id="0702a11"></a>道理設許尒者沙應出油角應有乳故成非理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如<a 
name="0702a12" id="0702a12"></a>是詰<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>至法界耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四界具有無文分為二先難<a 
name="0702a13" id="0702a13"></a>後破此初難云既齊有情應皆具界界若具者何不<a 
name="0702a14" id="0702a14"></a>許有涅槃界耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論應詰彼言至不應道理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0702b01" id="0702b01"></a>破之中文分為二一二界相違破有無二界既<span class="gaiji">[牙-(必-心)+?]<!--gaiji,,1[牙-(必-心)+?],2&#x3E26;,3--></span>相違<a 
name="0702b02" id="0702b02"></a>如何得言無姓之中許有有姓<span class="gaiji">[牙-(必-心)+?]<!--gaiji,,1[牙-(必-心)+?],2&#x3E26;,3--></span>相違故猶如苦樂性<a 
name="0702b03" id="0702b03"></a>非相有二無非有性破若言二界<span class="gaiji">[牙-(必-心)+?]<!--gaiji,,1[牙-(必-心)+?],2&#x3E26;,3--></span>不違者許無姓中<a 
name="0702b04" id="0702b04"></a>立其有姓亦為不可是相違故違自之失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是詰<a 
name="0702b05" id="0702b05"></a><span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>至種姓耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五辯生後姓文分為二先難後破<a 
name="0702b06" id="0702b06"></a>此初舉喻難無令有。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論應詰彼言至定種姓耶。</p><a 
name="0702b07" id="0702b07"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後破文二一理無轉有破二縱轉無成破初中有二<a 
name="0702b08" id="0702b08"></a>先徵後破此雙徵也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若言尒者至不應道理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0702b09" id="0702b09"></a>曰後破文二一若言尒下無果定義失汝若復言先有三<a 
name="0702b10" id="0702b10"></a>乘姓後無三姓者順解脫分善根應當無果以無性故<a 
name="0702b11" id="0702b11"></a>猶如兔角又若尒者不可言定先有後無不名定故二<a 
name="0702b12" id="0702b12"></a>若不尒下法喻例同失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又應責彼至後生耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0702b13" id="0702b13"></a>曰二縱轉無成破文分為二先縱後破此先縱許而<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span><a 
name="0703a01" id="0703a01"></a>定也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若言即於至不應道理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後破之中文<a 
name="0703a02" id="0703a02"></a>分為二一現轉不成破二後轉亦非破初破文三牒徵<a 
name="0703a03" id="0703a03"></a>及破破中有二一脫分無姓失何有現生能起脫分名<a 
name="0703a04" id="0703a04"></a>無姓耶二非劣轉勝失現不能起順脫善根如何能<a 
name="0703a05" id="0703a05"></a>起般涅槃耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若言後生至不應道理。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二後<a 
name="0703a06" id="0703a06"></a>轉亦非破文亦分三謂牒徵破破中有二一先集後成<a 
name="0703a07" id="0703a07"></a>失若此生中<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>集善根應即此生成涅槃法何待後<a 
name="0703a08" id="0703a08"></a>生而方轉耶又後生善而應無有涅槃法果是善<a 
name="0703a09" id="0703a09"></a>根故如此生善二不集例成先若也此生先未集善此<a 
name="0703a10" id="0703a10"></a>生所以未轉成者後生亦然後生何因而許轉耶彼<a 
name="0703a11" id="0703a11"></a>此異因不可得故故為不可。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略有至眼聲聞。</p><a 
name="0703a12" id="0703a12"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯有種姓門文分為二一明類異二明證別初<a 
name="0703a13" id="0703a13"></a>文有四一摽二徵三列四釋此前三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若有安住至<a 
name="0703a14" id="0703a14"></a>生聲聞。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋如標文分為十十中合分為三初<a 
name="0703b01" id="0703b01"></a>明前四次明第五後明後五此前四也遇佛發心名為<a 
name="0703b02" id="0703b02"></a>入法染淨可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論末法時生至皆悉成就。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次<a 
name="0703b03" id="0703b03"></a>明第五末法聲聞分之為二一<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>名徵起二依徵正釋<a 
name="0703b04" id="0703b04"></a>釋中有三一明惡行二辯末時三彰惡果初中有二<a 
name="0703b05" id="0703b05"></a>先彰後結初有十八句一愛重利養二違背妙法三三<a 
name="0703b06" id="0703b06"></a>毒增盛四慳嫉等具五&#x8B1F;詐現前六為命出家七有<a 
name="0703b07" id="0703b07"></a>動無靜八迷亂性闇九諸惑現行十憂苦無猒十一<a 
name="0703b08" id="0703b08"></a>樂諠棄靜十二不修三學十三捨真樂俗十四謗正法<a 
name="0703b09" id="0703b09"></a>人十五犯淨尸羅無餘等者四他勝處名曰無餘由犯<a 
name="0703b10" id="0703b10"></a>根本枝等亦亡無餘僧用名無餘也十三僧殘名曰<a 
name="0703b11" id="0703b11"></a>有餘有出罪法容有僧用名有餘也十六結託&#x95D8;訟<a 
name="0703b12" id="0703b12"></a>十七染心度人十八為利敬薎處家慳等具誠實論<a 
name="0703b13" id="0703b13"></a>絢者字林云文盛也藻者水中之草有文者也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0704a01" id="0704a01"></a>法末時者至生那落迦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯末時三彰惡果。</p><a 
name="0704a02" id="0704a02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若有成就至清淨眼。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明後五初賢善中息<a 
name="0704a03" id="0704a03"></a>肉未生者如來出世十二年前未有犯戒名息肉未生<a 
name="0704a04" id="0704a04"></a>犯戒之人類同息肉餘文可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次或有至不能<a 
name="0704a05" id="0704a05"></a>證。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明證別文中有二先明根劣現未能證後<a 
name="0704a06" id="0704a06"></a>彰放逸亦不證知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次當釋至生無量福。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0704a07" id="0704a07"></a>三具戒生福門文分三分謂摽徵釋此初摽也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0704a08" id="0704a08"></a>何等為四至第四法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二徵三釋釋中有四一具<a 
name="0704a09" id="0704a09"></a>戒律儀二少欲生足三不擾同行四不求他知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復<a 
name="0704a10" id="0704a10"></a>次若有至隨煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四&#x5F83;他家法門文分為四一<a 
name="0704a11" id="0704a11"></a>摽二徵三列四釋此初三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中聲聞至倍令增<a 
name="0704a12" id="0704a12"></a>長。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋分二先釋斷除後彰勝利初中有三一<a 
name="0704a13" id="0704a13"></a>斷初隨惑二斷次隨惑三斷後隨惑此初文二先標<a 
name="0704a14" id="0704a14"></a>後釋釋中分六時時&#x5F83;等為第一相於可愛等為第二<a 
name="0704b01" id="0704b01"></a>相不以凶等為第三相善自守等為第四相又隨順<a 
name="0704b02" id="0704b02"></a>等為第五相猶如山岳為第六相不應受等與不應<a 
name="0704b03" id="0704b03"></a>觸義類相似故合為一非信信家皆所化處亦合為一<a 
name="0704b04" id="0704b04"></a>而言隨順遠離等者遠離謂即出世心也隨順等者<a 
name="0704b05" id="0704b05"></a>如次聞思及修慧也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又由六相至不毀呰。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0704b06" id="0704b06"></a>斷次隨惑文亦分二先摽後釋釋中有六一情無染著<a 
name="0704b07" id="0704b07"></a>二利無染著三無利不苦四不敬不苦五自他利等六<a 
name="0704b08" id="0704b08"></a>利無讚毀。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又由六相至故宣說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三斷後隨惑<a 
name="0704b09" id="0704b09"></a>亦具摽釋釋中亦六一不希他信二了知出離三起三<a 
name="0704b10" id="0704b10"></a>意樂四今脫苦難五妙達法性六諷誦真文引發等<a 
name="0704b11" id="0704b11"></a>三體雖各別意樂是同故合為一。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知初隨至為<a 
name="0704b12" id="0704b12"></a>究竟。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後彰勝利。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次當釋至清淨故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0704b13" id="0704b13"></a>曰五三處了知門文分為二初&#x60E3;標列後別解釋此初<a 
name="0705a01" id="0705a01"></a>摽列有三種也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何雜染至清淨所依。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0705a02" id="0705a02"></a>別釋中文分為二一別明二處二重明二法初中有三<a 
name="0705a03" id="0705a03"></a>一辯所依二明雜染三彰清淨此初復二先徵後釋<a 
name="0705a04" id="0705a04"></a>言此身者染淨二法所依身也有色身中惑種未滅<a 
name="0705a05" id="0705a05"></a>名為<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重愚夫即是趣於無明及雜染者諸有學者<a 
name="0705a06" id="0705a06"></a>名趣於明及清淨也清淨明者即無染也謂此色身<a 
name="0705a07" id="0705a07"></a>通與二人為所依止故名雜染清淨所依。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何雜染<a 
name="0705a08" id="0705a08"></a>至自體令生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明雜染能依愚夫由愚造業名<a 
name="0705a09" id="0705a09"></a>為雜染由此雜染淨不淨業為因緣故如次能感愛<a 
name="0705a10" id="0705a10"></a>非愛果及<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>非<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>善惡報生名自體起。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何清淨<a 
name="0705a11" id="0705a11"></a>至得離繫。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰清淨能依法中文分為二先徵<a 
name="0705a12" id="0705a12"></a>後釋釋中有二先摽後釋釋中又二一學證真智為<a 
name="0705a13" id="0705a13"></a>證如故二學斷惑智為斷惑故由此二能故於淨中<a 
name="0705a14" id="0705a14"></a>最為殊勝餘智兼俗故不明之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次即此至煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span><a 
name="0705b01" id="0705b01"></a>斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二重明二法文復分二先辯第三後明第一初<a 
name="0705b02" id="0705b02"></a>中有二一辯淨因二明淨果初中分四一標二徵三列四<a 
name="0705b03" id="0705b03"></a>釋此前三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中如來至對治故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋之中<a 
name="0705b04" id="0705b04"></a>文分為五一正說者二正行者三明正行四心所治五<a 
name="0705b05" id="0705b05"></a>慧所治此前三中由能斷惑名無上治。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論略有五<a 
name="0705b06" id="0705b06"></a>法至分別貪愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四心所治文分為二先摽後列列<a 
name="0705b07" id="0705b07"></a>中有五前四可知五順捨等分別貪也於所學中捨而<a 
name="0705b08" id="0705b08"></a>不習貪能隨順名順貪愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論略由三法至所有我<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>。</p><a 
name="0705b09" id="0705b09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五慧所治文分為二先摽後釋釋中分三一不了<a 
name="0705b10" id="0705b10"></a>法愚二諦中疑<span class="gaiji">網<!--gaiji,網,1[絅-口+又],2,3--></span>三修道我<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由於如是至極清<a 
name="0705b11" id="0705b11"></a>淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明淨果。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次於此至過患故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0705b12" id="0705b12"></a>明第一染淨所依文分為二初&#x60E3;標列後依摽釋此初<a 
name="0705b13" id="0705b13"></a>摽列而有三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由自性者至不同分相。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後依<a 
name="0706a01" id="0706a01"></a>摽釋文亦分三一明自性二辯因緣三明過患初中有二<a 
name="0706a02" id="0706a02"></a>先摽後釋釋中分三由有色者明第一相有情皆有<a 
name="0706a03" id="0706a03"></a>色有色之身故名共相由<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重者明第二相惑種勝劣<a 
name="0706a04" id="0706a04"></a>無堪任等有情各異名為自相由不淨等明第三相<a 
name="0706a05" id="0706a05"></a>雖彼人天皆有色身淨穢有異名不同分。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由因緣<a 
name="0706a06" id="0706a06"></a>者至之所長養。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯因緣文中有二先標後釋<a 
name="0706a07" id="0706a07"></a>釋中有三一共相因緣二令生因緣三令住因緣初共<a 
name="0706a08" id="0706a08"></a>因者凡有色身皆有四大故名為共生住各別&#x5C5E;<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;己]'>己</span><a 
name="0706a09" id="0706a09"></a>所因故名為自。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由過患者至名為磨滅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0706a10" id="0706a10"></a>三明過患文分為二初<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>摽列後依摽釋釋中逆次<a 
name="0706a11" id="0706a11"></a>先明苦性後辯無常燥者說文云乾也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次因思<a 
name="0706a12" id="0706a12"></a>至故還滅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六所知名事門文分為二先<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>經問<a 
name="0706a13" id="0706a13"></a>後廣辯釋釋中文二先辯後證辯中復二先略後廣此<a 
name="0706a14" id="0706a14"></a>義同前六十五中思慧地文<span class="gaiji">疏<!--gaiji,疏,1[跳-兆+(梳-木)],2&#x47FD;,3--></span><span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>明訖故不重釋問論<a 
name="0706b01" id="0706b01"></a>有何意前後重明荅前文為明所緣義故名等亦是<a 
name="0706b02" id="0706b02"></a>所緣中攝所以敘釋此辯聲聞所知學法名等亦是<a 
name="0706b03" id="0706b03"></a>所知等法故再敘之無重言失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次有四至如前<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span><a 
name="0706b04" id="0706b04"></a>說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰七辯緣四諦門文分為二一<span class="gaiji">總<!--gaiji,總,1[(牛*匆)/心],2&#x22770;,3--></span>摽指處二依<a 
name="0706b05" id="0706b05"></a>摽再釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若真實至非苦因。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二依<a 
name="0706b06" id="0706b06"></a>摽再釋文分為五一辯知四諦二彰起勤因三明斷作<a 
name="0706b07" id="0706b07"></a>證四彰&#x8B1F;過患五明<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>語失初辯諦中文分三&#x53DA;一辯<a 
name="0706b08" id="0706b08"></a>&#x60E3;名二別明四三&#x63D4;分別初中有二先徵後釋此初徵<a 
name="0706b09" id="0706b09"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至是苦因故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分三摽徵釋也謂<a 
name="0706b10" id="0706b10"></a>邪見等非真計真說為顛倒知是真邪名不顛倒所<a 
name="0706b11" id="0706b11"></a>以如次苦性苦因苦集諦攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次由二至滅壞義。</p><a 
name="0706b12" id="0706b12"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二別明四諦文即為四一苦二集三滅四道苦中<a 
name="0706b13" id="0706b13"></a>分三一彰苦四理二明理相即三問荅料揀初復分三<a 
name="0707a01" id="0707a01"></a>一理二教三明通達理中分四一顯無常二明苦義三彰空<a 
name="0707a02" id="0707a02"></a>義四無我義初中有三摽列及釋釋中有二一非有義<a 
name="0707a03" id="0707a03"></a>謂遍計性性常無故名曰無常二滅壞義諸行遷謝<a 
name="0707a04" id="0707a04"></a>名曰無常大乘理中具二無常小唯後一。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由二種相<a 
name="0707a05" id="0707a05"></a>至相轉義。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明苦義文分為二先摽後釋釋<a 
name="0707a06" id="0707a06"></a>中有二初相行苦所計我法無名非有妄執所熏名<a 
name="0707a07" id="0707a07"></a>執習等此習<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重在本識中而令諸行無有堪任名<a 
name="0707a08" id="0707a08"></a>行苦相次相八苦義思可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由二種相至遠離相義。</p><a 
name="0707a09" id="0707a09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰空義文分為二先摽後釋釋中有二謂補特<a 
name="0707a10" id="0707a10"></a>等遠離我法如次名為人法空義。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由二種相至無<a 
name="0707a11" id="0707a11"></a>我相義。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四無我義文分為二先摽後釋釋中有<a 
name="0707a12" id="0707a12"></a>二小乘無人大乘兼法寬狹不同故別摽舉問空及<a 
name="0707a13" id="0707a13"></a>無我皆言自性二何別耶　荅遠離我性說之為空無<a 
name="0707a14" id="0707a14"></a>有主宰目為無我。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復有二教至無始教。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明<a 
name="0707b01" id="0707b01"></a>諦教文中有二先摽後釋釋中有二一無常教說苦<a 
name="0707b02" id="0707b02"></a>諦中新熏因果前滅後生名無常教說本苦諦法尒<a 
name="0707b03" id="0707b03"></a>因果名無始教。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又有二種至界通達。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明通達<a 
name="0707b04" id="0707b04"></a>悟苦理事名達有為悟苦真如名達無為。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次由五<a 
name="0707b05" id="0707b05"></a>至所緣事故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明理相即文分為二一明即苦二<a 
name="0707b06" id="0707b06"></a>即無我此先明由五種因緣無常即苦一明攝受<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重<a 
name="0707b07" id="0707b07"></a>是苦無常既為<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>重所攝故即是苦二法性者無常<a 
name="0707b08" id="0707b08"></a>即以生等苦法而成其性所以即苦三隨逐者無常<a 
name="0707b09" id="0707b09"></a>諸行被苦所隨不能捨離所以名苦四由因等有漏蘊<a 
name="0707b10" id="0707b10"></a>等無常名行增長因者即是其苦行因苦增名為即<a 
name="0707b11" id="0707b11"></a>苦五執著等苦諦無常妄為常樂所以無常即為苦<a 
name="0707b12" id="0707b12"></a>攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次由五至相依故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二即無我亦有五因<a 
name="0707b13" id="0707b13"></a>一離苦等無我既離苦行叵得明知諸苦體即無我二<a 
name="0708a01" id="0708a01"></a>彼苦等彼苦諸行必依眾緣眾緣即是無我行也三<a 
name="0708a02" id="0708a02"></a>無作等彼苦諸行無實作用即無我義四<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span>那等<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span><a 
name="0708a03" id="0708a03"></a>那生者即無我也我謂常故五展轉等苦法展轉相<a 
name="0708a04" id="0708a04"></a>依而住不能獨立不獨立者即無我也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若苦<a 
name="0708a05" id="0708a05"></a>諦至苦諦攝耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三問荅料揀文別有六一明<a 
name="0708a06" id="0708a06"></a>苦諦攝違害等文分為二先問後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅<a 
name="0708a07" id="0708a07"></a>至所攝諸行。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅意云於三苦中唯彼苦苦<a 
name="0708a08" id="0708a08"></a>名不愛等餘二苦非故順後荅二。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問如佛世尊至行<a 
name="0708a09" id="0708a09"></a>苦性。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明八苦三苦所攝文分為二先問後荅此<a 
name="0708a10" id="0708a10"></a>初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至顯行苦性。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若<a 
name="0708a11" id="0708a11"></a>無常至無常耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明無常是苦非苦文亦分二<a 
name="0708a12" id="0708a12"></a>此先問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至行苦所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅分三摽<a 
name="0708a13" id="0708a13"></a>徵及釋釋中但辯無常非苦以諸道諦非三苦故。</p><a 
name="0708b01" id="0708b01"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若無常苦至無常非苦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四辯無常與空<a 
name="0708b02" id="0708b02"></a>異同文分為二先問後荅荅中有二先摽後釋苦集<a 
name="0708b03" id="0708b03"></a>具四諸無常苦皆空無我道諦除苦但有三種滅但<a 
name="0708b04" id="0708b04"></a>有二所以無我非無常苦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若無常苦至苦所摽<a 
name="0708b05" id="0708b05"></a>故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五辯無常與苦一異文分為二先問後荅荅中<a 
name="0708b06" id="0708b06"></a>有二先摽後釋釋中又二一明壞苦無常故苦二明苦<a 
name="0708b07" id="0708b07"></a>行自性故苦何以然者<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span><span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>性故苦所標故如次釋<a 
name="0708b08" id="0708b08"></a>後二苦因也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若是苦諦至苦諦耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六明<a 
name="0708b09" id="0708b09"></a>苦集兩法異同文分為二先問後荅此先問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0708b10" id="0708b10"></a>荅至苦諦所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅文二先摽後釋業及煩<a 
name="0708b11" id="0708b11"></a><span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>是集皆苦以皆具有逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>性故或有是苦而非是<a 
name="0708b12" id="0708b12"></a>集於中有二一無學身善無記法先業招故果名為<a 
name="0708b13" id="0708b13"></a>苦非感後因不名為集二異生身中三受俱行無記果<a 
name="0709a01" id="0709a01"></a>法皆名為苦體非善惡不名為集。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若猒患至<a 
name="0709a02" id="0709a02"></a>集諦所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明集諦文分為二一明分限二<a 
name="0709a03" id="0709a03"></a>彰勝劣初中有二先問後荅此初問云無始招感可<a 
name="0709a04" id="0709a04"></a>名為集而今資&#x7CAE;加行位中猒患發趣引出世間何<a 
name="0709a05" id="0709a05"></a>得名集。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至集諦所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅意云雖彼二<a 
name="0709a06" id="0709a06"></a>位世道自性猒背後有然能隨順後有三行修諸福<a 
name="0709a07" id="0709a07"></a>業故亦集攝未名非集問五十一云二位是道而非集<a 
name="0709a08" id="0709a08"></a>攝復云何通荅前據出世道諦資&#x7CAE;道攝非集此<a 
name="0709a09" id="0709a09"></a>據有漏順後有心故為集攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若一切至唯施<a 
name="0709a10" id="0709a10"></a>設愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰勝劣文分為二先問後荅此初也。</p><a 
name="0709a11" id="0709a11"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至無義利故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅分二先摽後釋此先<a 
name="0709a12" id="0709a12"></a>摽舉由有四義故唯說愛能起取者顯潤生愛能發<a 
name="0709a13" id="0709a13"></a>業者是業發愛遍諸事等如下自釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論遍諸事者至<a 
name="0709a14" id="0709a14"></a>當知亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二一明遍事二明無義初二易<a 
name="0709b01" id="0709b01"></a>故略不辯之先明遍事文復分二先釋後結釋中有四<a 
name="0709b02" id="0709b02"></a>一彰遍緣事二明受異同三明欲患法四明愛種類後<a 
name="0709b03" id="0709b03"></a>三雖事初得&#x60E3;名初遍事中文復分三一釋遍事名<a 
name="0709b04" id="0709b04"></a>二明愛行相三四句分別此初也謂現愛體亦名後有<a 
name="0709b05" id="0709b05"></a>喜貪等三遍緣諸境故得遍名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論順後有愛至諸<a 
name="0709b06" id="0709b06"></a>所有愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明愛行相文分為三初明後有次辯<a 
name="0709b07" id="0709b07"></a>喜貪後彰彼彼獨愛是&#x60E3;故不明之初後有中復分為<a 
name="0709b08" id="0709b08"></a>二一緣後有者希求後身發業愛也二是後因通潤生<a 
name="0709b09" id="0709b09"></a>愛次喜貪愛謂於現在<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得境中生喜愛也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若<a 
name="0709b10" id="0709b10"></a>是愛者至是第四句。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三四句分別有四問荅此初<a 
name="0709b11" id="0709b11"></a>文二先問後荅荅中有四初句是愛非後三者問求上<a 
name="0709b12" id="0709b12"></a>解脫而非染心何名為愛荅傳三藏釋實善法欲與愛<a 
name="0709b13" id="0709b13"></a>名說二句喜等不名愛者謂與喜等俱時愛想<span class="gaiji">惡<!--gaiji,惡,1[栗-木+心],2&#x22663;,3--></span>及癡<a 
name="0710a01" id="0710a01"></a>等從彼喜等得喜等名然體非貪不名為愛即此三愛<a 
name="0710a02" id="0710a02"></a>是第三句者即此後有喜貪彼彼亦是愛也第四句者<a 
name="0710a03" id="0710a03"></a>有非後有亦非是愛謂於現在緣善心等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若<a 
name="0710a04" id="0710a04"></a>順後有至不和合愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二問荅以寬問狹故順<a 
name="0710a05" id="0710a05"></a>後荅喜俱行愛能招後報故亦順後憂俱等愛雖希<a 
name="0710a06" id="0710a06"></a>後有憂喜不並非喜貪俱。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若順後有至俱行愛。</p><a 
name="0710a07" id="0710a07"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第三問荅荅中有二初句可悉第二句者謂於未<a 
name="0710a08" id="0710a08"></a>得自內身起喜樂愛者謂於<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得外境而起即此喜<a 
name="0710a09" id="0710a09"></a>愛亦名後愛由斯境異故有後愛非彼彼愛言謂緣下<a 
name="0710a10" id="0710a10"></a>示後有愛非是彼彼愛之體也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若喜貪至第四句。</p><a 
name="0710a11" id="0710a11"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第四問荅初唯喜貪而非彼彼二唯彼彼而非喜貪<a 
name="0710a12" id="0710a12"></a>由未&#x51B3;定故無喜俱三俱句者緣此未來名彼彼由&#x51B3;<a 
name="0710a13" id="0710a13"></a>定故復有喜俱喜緣未來理無違故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若成就並<a 
name="0710a14" id="0710a14"></a>繫受耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明受異同文分為二一欲色對明二例<a 
name="0710b01" id="0710b01"></a>餘分別初中有二先問後荅此初問也愛依受生故因<a 
name="0710b02" id="0710b02"></a>辯也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至及滅盡定。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅之中句分為四<a 
name="0710b03" id="0710b03"></a>細尋可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如欲界繫至皆作四句。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二例餘分<a 
name="0710b04" id="0710b04"></a>別有五四句思之可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問諸妙欲至是士夫欲。</p><a 
name="0710b05" id="0710b05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明欲患法文分為二先問後荅荅中四句依人<a 
name="0710b06" id="0710b06"></a>辯釋如理應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次此愛至處差別故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四<a 
name="0710b07" id="0710b07"></a>明愛種類類別分三一愛用種類二界別種類三有無<a 
name="0710b08" id="0710b08"></a>種類初中有二一名有愛謂於現身起獨愛也二受用<a 
name="0710b09" id="0710b09"></a>者文中有二先標後釋釋中有二謂於<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得及未得<a 
name="0710b10" id="0710b10"></a>中如次喜貪及彼彼也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又即此愛至知亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0710b11" id="0710b11"></a>界別種類分之為三摽列及釋釋中有三欲界色界<a 
name="0710b12" id="0710b12"></a>及無色界如次應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論即此後有至及無有愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0710b13" id="0710b13"></a>三有無種類唯依後有立有無者謂計後內身有無<a 
name="0711a01" id="0711a01"></a>於愛現<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得之身不可生有無愛故於未來未知境<a 
name="0711a02" id="0711a02"></a>中生有無愛。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論是故此愛名遍諸事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二&#x60E3;結<a 
name="0711a03" id="0711a03"></a>前皆名遍事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何此愛至諸憂苦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明無<a 
name="0711a04" id="0711a04"></a>義文分為二先徵後釋釋中義別文分十五一一次第<a 
name="0711a05" id="0711a05"></a>尋之可知。</p><a 
name="0711a06" id="0711a06"></a><p style="margin-left: 2em"><span class="headname">論卷第六十八</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問諸行寂滅至行寂滅耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0711a07" id="0711a07"></a>曰三明滅諦文分為二一問荅分別二彰其正說問荅有<a 
name="0711a08" id="0711a08"></a>三初中有二先問後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至諸行寂滅。</p><a 
name="0711a09" id="0711a09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅之云諸行寂滅通擇非擇及無常滅滅諦<a 
name="0711a10" id="0711a10"></a>但是擇滅所&#x53CE;而非無常及非擇滅故諸行滅有非<a 
name="0711a11" id="0711a11"></a>滅諦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問何等法滅故名滅諦耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二問荅中文<a 
name="0711a12" id="0711a12"></a>分為二初問後荅此初問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至無餘依滅諦　<span title="未知的文字">▆</span>。</p><a 
name="0711a13" id="0711a13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅文二初&#x60E3;標列後別明之言依滅者苦依身<a 
name="0711a14" id="0711a14"></a>也問得擇滅者由斷縛法智證名得苦依非縛依滅<a 
name="0711b01" id="0711b01"></a>智亡云何得滅荅得有餘時無餘同得理無二故苦依<a 
name="0711b02" id="0711b02"></a>盡時無餘理顯故云後得實先<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若此滅諦<a 
name="0711b03" id="0711b03"></a>至般涅槃耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三問荅中文分為二初問後荅此<a 
name="0711b04" id="0711b04"></a>初問云若此滅諦先未斷惑滅相未生後斷惑時<a 
name="0711b05" id="0711b05"></a>方始言有何得是常設是常者一切有情何不皆證。</p><a 
name="0711b06" id="0711b06"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至非生所顯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅之云不流轉相是滅諦相<a 
name="0711b07" id="0711b07"></a>云何汝難先無後有有是流轉故又無生滅離體是常<a 
name="0711b08" id="0711b08"></a>然由有情斷惑所顯故有證者及未證者非皆證之亦<a 
name="0711b09" id="0711b09"></a>非後時生所顯也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次若有至<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>減過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰<a 
name="0711b10" id="0711b10"></a>其正說文分為四一標二徵三列四釋此初三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若言<a 
name="0711b11" id="0711b11"></a>諸行至增益過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋如標亦分為四一辯增益<a 
name="0711b12" id="0711b12"></a>過諸行盡處即名為滅不可說行與滅體異若執其滅<a 
name="0711b13" id="0711b13"></a>異行實有故成增過。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論言無異者至分別過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0712a01" id="0712a01"></a>二邪分別過行是有為滅是無為二種自相由來各異<a 
name="0712a02" id="0712a02"></a>今言不異名邪分別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論言亦有異至雜亂過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0712a03" id="0712a03"></a>三相雜亂過有異無異法應成雜若許尒者即應一法<a 
name="0712a04" id="0712a04"></a>亦苦亦樂。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論言非有異至<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>減過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四法<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span><a 
name="0712a05" id="0712a05"></a>減過異不異法皆&#x60E3;撥無故成<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>減能離四者即成正<a 
name="0712a06" id="0712a06"></a>說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若唯一切至而為道諦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明道諦文<a 
name="0712a07" id="0712a07"></a>分為二一正明諦相二辯餘道攝初文有三一辯說八<a 
name="0712a08" id="0712a08"></a>支二彰斷煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>三明無相行初文分二一辯聖八支二<a 
name="0712a09" id="0712a09"></a>明見差別初中有二先徵後釋此初也五取蘊者無漏<a 
name="0712a10" id="0712a10"></a>五蘊也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至而起修學。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二初約學<a 
name="0712a11" id="0712a11"></a>明後依蘊說此初也實無漏蘊皆是道諦由八道支<a 
name="0712a12" id="0712a12"></a>三學所攝故偏明也三學攝八即下三蘊攝支是也。</p><a 
name="0712a13" id="0712a13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又此八聖至名道諦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後依蘊說文分為二初&#x60E3;<a 
name="0712a14" id="0712a14"></a>略明後別徵釋此略明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問何因緣故至說為戒<a 
name="0712b01" id="0712b01"></a>蘊。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別徵釋文分三分初明戒蘊次明慧蘊<a 
name="0712b02" id="0712b02"></a>後明定蘊初中有二先問後荅此先<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>經而起問也。</p><a 
name="0712b03" id="0712b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至受用財故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅之中文分為二一正荅所<a 
name="0712b04" id="0712b04"></a>徵二引異名證初中有二先&#x60E3;摽列後依摽釋此初<a 
name="0712b05" id="0712b05"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂正語至受用法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後依摽釋文分為二<a 
name="0712b06" id="0712b06"></a>一明受法二釋受財初中有二先釋後結謂正語業受<a 
name="0712b07" id="0712b07"></a>用法時由戒為依故戒蘊攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由正命故至受用財。</p><a 
name="0712b08" id="0712b08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二釋受財文亦為二先釋後結謂此正命能離邪<a 
name="0712b09" id="0712b09"></a>求正受財者為由有戒為依止故故說戒攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又於<a 
name="0712b10" id="0712b10"></a>是處至意現行性。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二引異名證文分為二先引聖<a 
name="0712b11" id="0712b11"></a>言後依教釋此初也言是處者是彼正語正業命處<a 
name="0712b12" id="0712b12"></a>即說此三名增上淨意現行性。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中依止至意現行<a 
name="0712b13" id="0712b13"></a>性。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後依教釋文中有二先彰所離後釋淨名文<a 
name="0713a01" id="0713a01"></a>可知也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問何因緣故至說為慧蘊。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次明慧<a 
name="0713a02" id="0713a02"></a>蘊文分為二先問後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至而得究竟。</p><a 
name="0713a03" id="0713a03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅之中具摽釋結釋中有三一通真義真俗<a 
name="0713a04" id="0713a04"></a>諦也二說真義說真俗也三斷餘結斷後惑也此慧<a 
name="0713a05" id="0713a05"></a>三業如次由於正見等三助之方成故說此三慧蘊中<a 
name="0713a06" id="0713a06"></a>攝有處說勤通於定慧此唯慧者據助慧勝故偏<a 
name="0713a07" id="0713a07"></a>說也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問何因緣至為定蘊。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明定蘊文中<a 
name="0713a08" id="0713a08"></a>有二先問後荅此先問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至為定所依。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0713a09" id="0713a09"></a>後荅分二初<span class="gaiji">總<!--gaiji,總,1[(牛*匆)/心],2&#x22770;,3--></span>摽列後別解釋釋中有二先明自性<a 
name="0713a10" id="0713a10"></a>後辯所依所依分三摽釋及結。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次正見至能離<a 
name="0713a11" id="0713a11"></a>結見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明見差別文分三&#x53DA;一彰差別二會違文<a 
name="0713a12" id="0713a12"></a>三明相攝初中又三一摽二列三依摽釋此初摽舉而<a 
name="0713a13" id="0713a13"></a>有十一列中有六影餘五種名為乃至。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於四種行至<a 
name="0713a14" id="0713a14"></a>苦諦正見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三依摽釋文分為二初明前八後辯<a 
name="0713b01" id="0713b01"></a>後三初中有二先釋後結釋中又二先觀病行後觀<a 
name="0713b02" id="0713b02"></a>生滅初中有四謂病<span class="gaiji">癰<!--gaiji,癰,1[病-丙+(雍-〦)],2&#x3FC8;,3--></span>等煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>現行如病盛發隨眠<a 
name="0713b03" id="0713b03"></a><span class="gaiji">[穴/侵]<!--gaiji,,1[穴/侵],2,3--></span>伏故如<span class="gaiji">癰<!--gaiji,癰,1[病-丙+(雍-〦)],2&#x3FC8;,3--></span>腫貪愛不遂如被箭中患妨出離故如障<a 
name="0713b04" id="0713b04"></a>隔後觀生滅及結可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若於集諦至所顯故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0713b05" id="0713b05"></a>後辯後三文可知矣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問若先起至如病等見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0713b06" id="0713b06"></a>二會違文分之為二先徵後釋此初徵云依餘教中先<a 
name="0713b07" id="0713b07"></a>說無常後觀病行今此異彼而何意耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至說彼<a 
name="0713b08" id="0713b08"></a>為先。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋之中文分三分一摽二徵三釋所以此<a 
name="0713b09" id="0713b09"></a>初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論何以故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二徵何意<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得道者而須先觀<a 
name="0713b10" id="0713b10"></a>如病等耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>得聖道至無我見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋所以<a 
name="0713b11" id="0713b11"></a>文分為二一論主明自先說病因二雙彰經論說先後<a 
name="0713b12" id="0713b12"></a>意此初也修道智見名為上位斷惑後起名為清淨。</p><a 
name="0713b13" id="0713b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知此中至常等見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二雙彰經論說先後意文<a 
name="0714a01" id="0714a01"></a>復分二先標後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論一是女病至所未得故。</p><a 
name="0714a02" id="0714a02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二先彰經說後明論說此明經說無常先<a 
name="0714a03" id="0714a03"></a>因即病等見是為能依無常等見是所依法加行等<a 
name="0714a04" id="0714a04"></a>位無常等見未斷惑故名不清淨以此等者此前無<a 
name="0714a05" id="0714a05"></a>常不淨見等經依此義先說無常。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論二是如病等至<a 
name="0714a06" id="0714a06"></a>善解脫故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明論說病等先因病等見者是所<a 
name="0714a07" id="0714a07"></a>依見能依見者即無常等<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>斷惑故名為清淨論依此義<a 
name="0714a08" id="0714a08"></a>先說病等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是十一至離繫行見。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明相攝十<a 
name="0714a09" id="0714a09"></a>一見中第七空見第八無我空門中攝第十一見無相門<a 
name="0714a10" id="0714a10"></a>攝餘之八見無願門攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次於修至一切煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>。</p><a 
name="0714a11" id="0714a11"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰斷煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>文中有三摽徵及釋此依預流後超<a 
name="0714a12" id="0714a12"></a>中二果所斷惑說不分三界現不現惑名曰一團起一無<a 
name="0714a13" id="0714a13"></a>閒或九無閒斷盡便登勝無學位不經中一故說為超<a 
name="0714a14" id="0714a14"></a>廣如唯識雜集二論及前應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次彼諸至斷煩<a 
name="0714b01" id="0714b01"></a><span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明無相行文分為三標徵及釋義思可知。</p><a 
name="0714b02" id="0714b02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次五神通至皆道諦攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯餘道攝有為<a 
name="0714b03" id="0714b03"></a>無漏諸功德等皆道諦攝前來第二別明諦訖。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0714b04" id="0714b04"></a>問一切四諦至是應遍知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三&#x60E3;分別文分為二先<a 
name="0714b05" id="0714b05"></a>辯斷知後明現觀初中又二一辯遍知二明永斷初中有<a 
name="0714b06" id="0714b06"></a>三先問次荅後&#x60E3;結之此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至是應遍知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0714b07" id="0714b07"></a>曰次荅及結苦二相者三苦等苦名苦自相空無我等<a 
name="0714b08" id="0714b08"></a>名為共相苦諦觀二故得遍名餘觀非共不名為遍。</p><a 
name="0714b09" id="0714b09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問苦諦亦應至應永斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明永斷分之為三<a 
name="0714b10" id="0714b10"></a>問荅及結文可知也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次於諸至煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>斷滅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0714b11" id="0714b11"></a>明現觀文分為二初摽後釋釋中有二一智現觀二斷現<a 
name="0714b12" id="0714b12"></a>觀現觀是智滅理體非今言觀者從能證說體實非也。</p><a 
name="0714b13" id="0714b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略有至前後差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰起勤因文分為<a 
name="0715a01" id="0715a01"></a>二初摽後釋釋中有五一說正法為說法故所以起<a 
name="0715a02" id="0715a02"></a>勤二共住者與修行者而共住故見賢思齊故發勤<a 
name="0715a03" id="0715a03"></a>也三四可知五智別者智自所證前劣後勝所以發勤<a 
name="0715a04" id="0715a04"></a>希後勝法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略有至永斷作證。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰斷<a 
name="0715a05" id="0715a05"></a>作證文分為二一明斷證二明離繫此初有二先摽後<a 
name="0715a06" id="0715a06"></a>列。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知離繫至相&#x5C5E;離繫。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明離繫亦具<a 
name="0715a07" id="0715a07"></a>標列列中有二一品別離繫謂斷迷理煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>所證無<a 
name="0715a08" id="0715a08"></a>為二相&#x5C5E;離繫斷迷事惑得擇滅也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問如世尊言<a 
name="0715a09" id="0715a09"></a>至不令行&#x8B1F;。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四彰&#x8B1F;過患文分為二先問後荅<a 
name="0715a10" id="0715a10"></a>此先<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>經而起問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至生那落迦。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅<a 
name="0715a11" id="0715a11"></a>之中文分為二一&#x60E3;彰&#x8B1F;過二別明&#x8B1F;行此初有二先<a 
name="0715a12" id="0715a12"></a>摽後列列有十二文易可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次欲界至七種<a 
name="0715a13" id="0715a13"></a>事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二別明&#x8B1F;行文分三分初摽次列後依摽<a 
name="0715a14" id="0715a14"></a>釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何八行至艱辛事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次列分二<a 
name="0715b01" id="0715b01"></a>先八後七各具徵列。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由初事故至乃至悶絕。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0715b02" id="0715b02"></a>曰後釋八七然彼八行依七事生先舉其事後彰其行<a 
name="0715b03" id="0715b03"></a>相對而明尋可知也然八行中除三顯示餘七與事合<a 
name="0715b04" id="0715b04"></a>而明之故但為七七箇又字即為七也顯示類同故不<a 
name="0715b05" id="0715b05"></a>別釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>語至復清淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五明<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>語失文<a 
name="0715b06" id="0715b06"></a>分為二先&#x60E3;後別此初&#x60E3;顯<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>語過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又有九種<a 
name="0715b07" id="0715b07"></a>至第九相。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別明中文分為二一辯<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>語相二<a 
name="0715b08" id="0715b08"></a>明語起處此初有三謂摽徵釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中略有至補特<a 
name="0715b09" id="0715b09"></a>伽羅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明語起處二差別也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次本地至今<a 
name="0715b10" id="0715b10"></a>當&#x51B3;擇。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二辯戒差別門文分為二一摽所<a 
name="0715b11" id="0715b11"></a>釋二正決擇此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論嗢&#x62D5;南曰至說喻事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0715b12" id="0715b12"></a>二正決擇文復分二初&#x60E3;摽章後依摽釋此頌摽中<a 
name="0715b13" id="0715b13"></a>門分十三一明攝法二明制立三辯尸羅四明無逸五明<a 
name="0716a01" id="0716a01"></a>障法六明學處七明觀察八明依處九明攝受十明受<a 
name="0716a02" id="0716a02"></a>用十一甚深十二明說十三喻事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論略有七處至七出<a 
name="0716a03" id="0716a03"></a>罪。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後依摽釋門亦十三一攝戒律儀門文分為四<a 
name="0716a04" id="0716a04"></a>一摽二徵三列四釋此初三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何教&#x52D1;至無邊。</p><a 
name="0716a05" id="0716a05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋如標亦分為七一明教&#x52D1;文具徵釋義思<a 
name="0716a06" id="0716a06"></a>可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何開聽至資生因緣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明開許聽<a 
name="0716a07" id="0716a07"></a>猶許也如開下士百一恭身資具等事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何制止<a 
name="0716a08" id="0716a08"></a>至違無罪法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明制止性罪可知犯遮罪名<a 
name="0716a09" id="0716a09"></a>違無罪法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何犯處至知其相。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明犯處文<a 
name="0716a10" id="0716a10"></a>分為二先徵後釋釋中分三標列及釋犯因而起名<a 
name="0716a11" id="0716a11"></a>處三業亦是起罪因緣亦名處也六戒壞者犯輕重戒<a 
name="0716a12" id="0716a12"></a>七見壞者起邪見也八軓則壞左右<span class="gaiji">[(厂@((既-旡)-日+口))*頁]<!--gaiji,,1[(厂@((既-旡)-日+口))*頁],2,3--></span>視失威儀等九<a 
name="0716a13" id="0716a13"></a>正命壞高聲現威起邪命也十隨護他心隨順他心<a 
name="0716a14" id="0716a14"></a>而犯禁戒如須提那子隨妻母心故犯重也十一護他<a 
name="0716b01" id="0716b01"></a><span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span><span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>如昔比丘見鵝吞珠荅云不見為護<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>他故犯<a 
name="0716b02" id="0716b02"></a>妄語十二護非處疑慮如有比丘入<span class="gaiji">[婬-壬+(工/山)]<!--gaiji,,1[婬-壬+(工/山)],2,3--></span>肆來荅云不去<a 
name="0716b03" id="0716b03"></a>斷他疑故而行妄語不善者下逐難偏釋至九十九<a 
name="0716b04" id="0716b04"></a>當具釋之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何有犯至當廣說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五明有犯<a 
name="0716b05" id="0716b05"></a>文分為二初明犯法後釋犯人初中有四一摽一徵三釋<a 
name="0716b06" id="0716b06"></a>四指釋中有五謂五因故所以有犯一因緣者犯罪因<a 
name="0716b07" id="0716b07"></a>也九十九云有四因緣犯所犯罪一無知故二放逸故三<a 
name="0716b08" id="0716b08"></a>煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>熾盛故四輕<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>故二發起者由等起心有三品故<a 
name="0716b09" id="0716b09"></a>故所犯罪成上中下九十九云由意樂者謂由下品貪<a 
name="0716b10" id="0716b10"></a>嗔癡纏所犯眾罪是下品罪中上亦尒三事故者所犯<a 
name="0716b11" id="0716b11"></a>境事有犯殺者依有情事盜依財等餘皆准知四<a 
name="0716b12" id="0716b12"></a>方便者所犯之戒前方便也五究竟者所犯事成名<a 
name="0716b13" id="0716b13"></a>為究竟其所指文如九十九初云應知略有五種罪聚<a 
name="0717a01" id="0717a01"></a>攝一切罪等下自廣明故不懸敘。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復有九種至有<a 
name="0717a02" id="0717a02"></a>學犯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋犯人文分為二先有後無此明九人有<a 
name="0717a03" id="0717a03"></a>所犯也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論無有無學至犯染汙罪。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明無犯文<a 
name="0717a04" id="0717a04"></a>分為二先摽後釋言小及隨小者戒中而有受二別言<a 
name="0717a05" id="0717a05"></a>顯受諸小輕戒及隨小顯彼輕戒一切學處悉皆止<a 
name="0717a06" id="0717a06"></a>息。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何無犯至苦受所逼。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六明無犯文具<a 
name="0717a07" id="0717a07"></a>徵列列中有四一初業者初學比丘未有所識佛言<a 
name="0717a08" id="0717a08"></a>不犯須提那子即其事也餘三可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何出罪至<a 
name="0717a09" id="0717a09"></a>命終<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰七明出罪文中有三徵列及釋釋中有<a 
name="0717a10" id="0717a10"></a>五一由自者如犯小罪自悔前非息後起意其罪得<a 
name="0717a11" id="0717a11"></a>出名為由自二由他者如善心者拔佛前草對一人悔<a 
name="0717a12" id="0717a12"></a>罪即出故三由自他者隨善惡心有所違犯名染不染<a 
name="0717a13" id="0717a13"></a>自責及他名由自他四轉依者謂苾&#x84AD;身犯苾&#x84AD;戒<a 
name="0717a14" id="0717a14"></a>轉為尼時其苾&#x84AD;罪自然而出何以然者以彼尼身<a 
name="0717b01" id="0717b01"></a>不可制犯苾&#x84AD;罪故轉為二形及轉失根彼皆捨戒<a 
name="0717b02" id="0717b02"></a>戒既捨<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>罪無所犯亦名為出五依捨者命終捨戒<a 
name="0717b03" id="0717b03"></a>戒體既無無犯名出。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略有至不斷清淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0717b04" id="0717b04"></a>曰二制立學處門文二番釋初中有二先摽後列列中<a 
name="0717b05" id="0717b05"></a>有十一道理淨斷惡進修令出離故二果清淨究竟令<a 
name="0717b06" id="0717b06"></a>得出世果故三攝受淨攝受財法離染名淨四外清<a 
name="0717b07" id="0717b07"></a>淨外塵不染五內清淨諸根無過六具分淨具前二也<a 
name="0717b08" id="0717b08"></a>七愛敬淨愛人敬法八伏治淨伏現染也九斷治淨斷<a 
name="0717b09" id="0717b09"></a>染種也十相續淨前因後果性成就也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復有差別<a 
name="0717b10" id="0717b10"></a>至正法清淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二番釋文中有二初摽後列列<a 
name="0717b11" id="0717b11"></a>中有十文易可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略有至邪禁過失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0717b12" id="0717b12"></a>三毗尼過失門文分為二先失後德此初文二先標後<a 
name="0717b13" id="0717b13"></a>列列中有十一壞學過失於所學處而不學故二不<a 
name="0718a01" id="0718a01"></a>喜過失於所學戒心不忍可三伴相違失於同法<a 
name="0718a02" id="0718a02"></a>者言行異故四期願過失所持淨戒期世果故餘文<a 
name="0718a03" id="0718a03"></a>可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復有十種至無上尸羅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明功德文具<a 
name="0718a04" id="0718a04"></a>標列列中有十一和合者理事和也二無間者無表<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span><a 
name="0718a05" id="0718a05"></a>那倍增故三無怨者於物不<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>故無怨對四無<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>害者<a 
name="0718a06" id="0718a06"></a>由戒遮止無<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>害心五堅固者久修習者戒性成就名<a 
name="0718a07" id="0718a07"></a>為堅固六出離者乘戒因緣出離世故七勝所治者<a 
name="0718a08" id="0718a08"></a>勝所對治犯戒垢也八不退者謂經四種不退位故九<a 
name="0718a09" id="0718a09"></a>不共者不共外道同所持也十無上者大乘尸羅非小<a 
name="0718a10" id="0718a10"></a>有也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次於毗至究竟時。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四勤學無逸門<a 
name="0718a11" id="0718a11"></a>文分為四標徵列釋此前三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何於毗至不放逸。</p><a 
name="0718a12" id="0718a12"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋如摽亦分為十一辯犯時文中有三謂徵釋<a 
name="0718a13" id="0718a13"></a>結五支如前本地分中第十七說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何至第二時等。</p><a 
name="0718a14" id="0718a14"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯定時文分三分謂徵釋結釋中有二初由修<a 
name="0718b01" id="0718b01"></a>習止舉捨三故不放逸後於得定不生愛等故不放<a 
name="0718b02" id="0718b02"></a>逸初中有三一明&#x76D6;生當即除捨二彼由下明&#x76D6;過患<a 
name="0718b03" id="0718b03"></a>三為欲下明將斷&#x76D6;修止舉捨止舉捨義如下當知。</p><a 
name="0718b04" id="0718b04"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何至第三時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三辯生時文分三&#x53DA;謂徵<a 
name="0718b05" id="0718b05"></a>釋結釋中有三一摽加行二正發起三加行德言依生<a 
name="0718b06" id="0718b06"></a>者依將結生名為生也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何至第四時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0718b07" id="0718b07"></a>四乞食時文顯可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何至第五時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五辯<a 
name="0718b08" id="0718b08"></a>作時由不放逸所燒&#x7151;物無燋爛失餘准此知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云<a 
name="0718b09" id="0718b09"></a>何至第六時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六明用時文易可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何至<a 
name="0718b10" id="0718b10"></a>第七時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰七辯求時文分三分徵釋及結釋<a 
name="0718b11" id="0718b11"></a>中有四一求世言二求真典三除勝負四明自益求真<a 
name="0718b12" id="0718b12"></a>典中甚深等者真如教也相似深者二空教也經典<a 
name="0718b13" id="0718b13"></a>之言通上分別求此等時心無動亂名不放逸。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云<a 
name="0719a01" id="0719a01"></a>何至第八時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰八辯思時如文可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何<a 
name="0719a02" id="0719a02"></a>至第九時等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰九遠離時。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何至修不放逸。</p><a 
name="0719a03" id="0719a03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十通達時具徵釋結文顯可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次有四<a 
name="0719a04" id="0719a04"></a>至荅如是等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五出家障礙門文分三分摽列<a 
name="0719a05" id="0719a05"></a>及釋釋中有四初意樂者意樂處俗不樂出家雖王<a 
name="0719a06" id="0719a06"></a>所逼無真出意名意樂障餘文可知若蘭所得者縱<a 
name="0719a07" id="0719a07"></a>失曰蘭。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略有至別解脫經。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六所應學處<a 
name="0719a08" id="0719a08"></a>門文分為四一摽二徵三列四釋此初三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論有犯無<a 
name="0719a09" id="0719a09"></a>犯至名為輕罪。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋分四一明有犯二明無犯三<a 
name="0719a10" id="0719a10"></a>明犯重四辯犯輕解脫戒經略不言也初二如前故不重<a 
name="0719a11" id="0719a11"></a>辯三犯重中而有六別一立別者如五犯聚佛立初聚<a 
name="0719a12" id="0719a12"></a>最為其重二事別者性遮二事而不同故性罪成重<a 
name="0719a13" id="0719a13"></a>餘文可知四犯輕者與重相違可知其相。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次諸持<a 
name="0719a14" id="0719a14"></a>至現行故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰七五相觀察門文分為五一摽二徵三<a 
name="0719b01" id="0719b01"></a>列四釋五&#x60E3;結之此前三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中一向至令不犯。</p><a 
name="0719b02" id="0719b02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋之中文分為五一明雜染二辯不行三明依<a 
name="0719b03" id="0719b03"></a>處四明過失五非一向此初一向雜染犯中謂性罪者<a 
name="0719b04" id="0719b04"></a>必皆雜染故令不犯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若毀犯者至速悔除。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0719b05" id="0719b05"></a>曰二辯不行有毀犯者令速悔除不令再起名為一向不<a 
name="0719b06" id="0719b06"></a>行<span title="未知的文字">▆</span>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又佛世尊至遮罪學處。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明依處<a 
name="0719b07" id="0719b07"></a>隨其根&#x519D;依其方處制立遮罪學處別也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若有<a 
name="0719b08" id="0719b08"></a>所餘至對治之法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明過失觀所餘器時方之<a 
name="0719b09" id="0719b09"></a><span class="gaiji">宜<!--gaiji,宜,1[冗-几+旦],2,3--></span>有犯過起同前第三制立之法而對治也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若有不<a 
name="0719b10" id="0719b10"></a>犯至治之法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五非一向由彼不犯是故不須一向<a 
name="0719b11" id="0719b11"></a>行於對治法也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是名為至觀察所犯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五&#x60E3;<a 
name="0719b12" id="0719b12"></a>結也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次至應修方便。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰八依處修習門文分<a 
name="0719b13" id="0719b13"></a>三分一摽二徵三釋依止此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何依止至修方便。</p><a 
name="0720a01" id="0720a01"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二徵修處。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂依止大師至藥什物。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三釋<a 
name="0720a02" id="0720a02"></a>依止文分為二先明七處後明六處此七分二前三依人<a 
name="0720a03" id="0720a03"></a>後四依具夫修道者必仗於師及資身具師若無者<a 
name="0720a04" id="0720a04"></a>善惡誰示資若闕者身何得安所以七處並名依處。</p><a 
name="0720a05" id="0720a05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於法至應修方便。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明六處先列後釋此列<a 
name="0720a06" id="0720a06"></a>六也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此中法者至非處善巧。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分六一明<a 
name="0720a07" id="0720a07"></a>其法二明學體三教授教誡教授善法教誡惡法四<a 
name="0720a08" id="0720a08"></a>辯等持五明供養先財後法法供養中言所餘者財<a 
name="0720a09" id="0720a09"></a>供之餘皆名法也六不放逸五善巧者如本地分二十七<a 
name="0720a10" id="0720a10"></a>釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次至五為他受。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰九五種攝受門文分為二<a 
name="0720a11" id="0720a11"></a>初&#x60E3;摽列後依摽釋此初也受衣&#x9262;等將&#x5C5E;<span class="corr" title='[已&gt;己]'>己</span>身名<a 
name="0720a12" id="0720a12"></a>&#x5C5E;<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;己]'>己</span>受如承眾命知眾僧事因得財利名承受受受他<a 
name="0720a13" id="0720a13"></a>寄物名委寄受為捨施故而受他物名捨施受本人不<a 
name="0720a14" id="0720a14"></a>在權為領納名為他受。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由二因緣至得清淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0720b01" id="0720b01"></a>曰後依摽釋文分為五二承受中非處等者屏處等也<a 
name="0720b02" id="0720b02"></a>言非量者過量受也不依僧法名非法受餘文可知。</p><a 
name="0720b03" id="0720b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次至不作淨故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十受用非淨門文分三&#x53DA;摽<a 
name="0720b04" id="0720b04"></a>列及釋此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論性有罪者至名為清淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0720b05" id="0720b05"></a>後釋分二先明不淨後明清淨初中有五一餘有罪二<a 
name="0720b06" id="0720b06"></a>不端嚴三不任用四非攝&#x5C5E;五不作淨復分為五一受得淨<a 
name="0720b07" id="0720b07"></a>謂受三衣及食等物二<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>壞者如穀&#x83D3;等三委寄淨四<a 
name="0720b08" id="0720b08"></a>時法淨如七曰藥等曰未滿時皆名為淨五捨分別<a 
name="0720b09" id="0720b09"></a>淨如受賊施物但作施心不應分別作賊等想名淨<a 
name="0720b10" id="0720b10"></a>應受後明清淨返上五種應知其相言賄貨者周禮注<a 
name="0720b11" id="0720b11"></a>云金玉曰貨布帛曰賄。</p><a 
name="0720b12" id="0720b12"></a><p style="margin-left: 2em"><span class="headname">論卷第六十九</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次應知至羯磨制立。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十一<a 
name="0720b13" id="0720b13"></a>甚深制立門文分為二一辯五真二明五偽真中有三<a 
name="0721a01" id="0721a01"></a>摽列及釋此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略由至不行故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0721a02" id="0721a02"></a>後釋之中文分為五一彰學制立二明犯制立三出<a 
name="0721a03" id="0721a03"></a>離制立四止息制立五羯磨制立初學制中文分三<a 
name="0721a04" id="0721a04"></a>分謂摽列釋此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論言自在者至制立學處。</p><a 
name="0721a05" id="0721a05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分五一明自在二不自在三戒壞失四鄙業<a 
name="0721a06" id="0721a06"></a>失五觀二失。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略由至最甚深。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明犯制<a 
name="0721a07" id="0721a07"></a>立文分三分一明犯制二彰意樂三思所犯初中有三謂<a 
name="0721a08" id="0721a08"></a>摽徵釋此初摽也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何為犯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次徵起也。</p><a 
name="0721a09" id="0721a09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂能障礙至不得生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二一明障礙二<a 
name="0721a10" id="0721a10"></a>明無障初文分二先略後廣此略明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知此障至<a 
name="0721a11" id="0721a11"></a>所知障。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後廣釋中文分為四一摽二列三別解釋<a 
name="0721a12" id="0721a12"></a>四彰次第此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>緩障者至名所知障。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0721a13" id="0721a13"></a>曰三別釋中文分為五一明<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>障二明罪障三輕<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>障<a 
name="0721a14" id="0721a14"></a>四惡作障五所知障一一行相尋文可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>緩障<a 
name="0721b01" id="0721b01"></a>至生次第。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四彰次第如文可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論與此相違至<a 
name="0721b02" id="0721b02"></a>所知障。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明無障。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次意樂至無引發欲。</p><a 
name="0721b03" id="0721b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰意樂文分為二一明毀壞二明具足初中有四<a 
name="0721b04" id="0721b04"></a>一摽二徵三列四釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次意樂至非治&#x7F78;故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0721b05" id="0721b05"></a>明具足文分為二初釋後證釋中有三謂摽徵列列中<a 
name="0721b06" id="0721b06"></a>有五文顯可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次應由至求所犯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三思所<a 
name="0721b07" id="0721b07"></a>犯文分為二先標後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂由別解脫法故。</p><a 
name="0721b08" id="0721b08"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋十處文即為十一辯略戒經。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由廣分別<a 
name="0721b09" id="0721b09"></a>毗柰耶故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明廣律教。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論五犯聚中由犯自<a 
name="0721b10" id="0721b10"></a>相故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰五犯聚即五篇也五中所犯一一各別名<a 
name="0721b11" id="0721b11"></a>為自相。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由六種差別至時差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明六差別<a 
name="0721b12" id="0721b12"></a>六差別義如六十八後具明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由無羞&#x803B;至殘相故。</p><a 
name="0721b13" id="0721b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五辯無羞&#x803B;波羅闍<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>迦者唐云他勝處善法<a 
name="0722a01" id="0722a01"></a>益<span class="corr" title='[已&gt;己]'>己</span>名之為自惡<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>於<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;己]'>己</span>立以他名由犯四重惡法增<a 
name="0722a02" id="0722a02"></a>強名他勝處所餘即是十三僧殘乃至眾學此所餘<a 
name="0722a03" id="0722a03"></a>等雖犯清禁而猶得有僧之餘分名曰僧殘不同初<a 
name="0722a04" id="0722a04"></a>篇全無僧分名他勝處梵云僧伽婆尸沙此云眾餘<a 
name="0722a05" id="0722a05"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由初業者至現所行故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六辯初非初初學比<a 
name="0722a06" id="0722a06"></a>丘久學比丘如次名初及非初業雖各有犯輕重有別<a 
name="0722a07" id="0722a07"></a>故分二類。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>出離故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰七明有逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>謂由<a 
name="0722a08" id="0722a08"></a>病等所逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>故雖有違犯而不成罪名為出離。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由<a 
name="0722a09" id="0722a09"></a>障難出離故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰八辯由障難謂命難等上樹過<a 
name="0722a10" id="0722a10"></a>人無有所犯亦名出離。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由有犯者至集僧眾故。</p><a 
name="0722a11" id="0722a11"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰九白師集眾以事白佛佛欲遮制故集於眾。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0722a12" id="0722a12"></a>由僧眾集至無<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>害故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十制立開許初雖&#x60E3;制<a 
name="0722a13" id="0722a13"></a>後隨根&#x519D;亦開許也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略由至悔出離故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0722a14" id="0722a14"></a>三出離制立文分三分一摽二列三各別釋此初二也。</p><a 
name="0722b01" id="0722b01"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論無染出離至無染出離。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三別釋中文分為二<a 
name="0722b02" id="0722b02"></a>一明五出離二彰小隨意初中有五一明無染二明逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span><a 
name="0722b03" id="0722b03"></a>三明障難四明無計五彰說悔初無染中文復分三<a 
name="0722b04" id="0722b04"></a><span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>釋及結如善心中採花供佛以善勝故<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>生之罪而<a 
name="0722b05" id="0722b05"></a>得減滅亦名出離。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>出離至逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>出離。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0722b06" id="0722b06"></a>曰二明逼<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>如被陵逼不成<span class="gaiji">[婬-壬+(工/山)]<!--gaiji,,1[婬-壬+(工/山)],2,3--></span>罪。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論障難出離至障<a 
name="0722b07" id="0722b07"></a>難出離。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明障難具<span class="gaiji">牒<!--gaiji,牒,1[牒-世+ㄊ],2&#x245CA;,3--></span>釋結謂遇命難馳走<a 
name="0722b08" id="0722b08"></a>失儀及上樹等皆無有過。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論無計出離至無計出離。</p><a 
name="0722b09" id="0722b09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明無計曠野等中遇命難等無計遣之揮刀<a 
name="0722b10" id="0722b10"></a>及杖亦無有犯。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論說悔出離至法悔除。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五彰說<a 
name="0722b11" id="0722b11"></a>悔除初篇外於餘犯中說悔也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論言小隨小至除性<a 
name="0722b12" id="0722b12"></a>罪。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰小隨意謂於遮戒犯小罪中如次根本<a 
name="0722b13" id="0722b13"></a>及前方便名小隨小。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略由至止息學處。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0723a01" id="0723a01"></a>四止息制立文分三分謂標列釋釋中有五一明清淨<a 
name="0723a02" id="0723a02"></a>二彰防壞三彰引接四彰教盛五遮難活由此五藏於<a 
name="0723a03" id="0723a03"></a>小學處權開不學名為止息。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次略由至白四羯<a 
name="0723a04" id="0723a04"></a>磨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五羯磨制立文分為二一明十羯磨二辯五<a 
name="0723a05" id="0723a05"></a>伽羅初中有三標徵及列列中有十一受具羯磨羯<a 
name="0723a06" id="0723a06"></a>磨梵語此云辦事受具戒時所施設者名受具羯<a 
name="0723a07" id="0723a07"></a>磨二者結界結大界等三者長養八戒羯磨名為長<a 
name="0723a08" id="0723a08"></a>養長初善心養後德故有云梵音布薩此云長養養<a 
name="0723a09" id="0723a09"></a>戒德故四同意者為所作事羯磨和僧僧眾意同名<a 
name="0723a10" id="0723a10"></a>為同意五趣向者諸有所&#x5F83;作法羯磨皆名趣向如尼<a 
name="0723a11" id="0723a11"></a>欲向僧邊受具及請自恣先於尼眾作法羯磨方趣<a 
name="0723a12" id="0723a12"></a>僧處名為趣向六恣舉者謂於自恣及舉罪時作羯<a 
name="0723a13" id="0723a13"></a>磨也七治&#x7F78;者治&#x7F78;惡人集眾作也八攝受者攝受弟<a 
name="0723a14" id="0723a14"></a>子初剃髮時集眾聽許亦為羯磨九十可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何<a 
name="0723b01" id="0723b01"></a>五種至補特伽羅。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯五伽羅文分為三謂徵<a 
name="0723b02" id="0723b02"></a>列釋此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何良慧至如書畫者。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋<a 
name="0723b03" id="0723b03"></a>分五一明良慧二明鸚鵡三彰炬燭四釋電光五明書<a 
name="0723b04" id="0723b04"></a>畫初良慧者於此等者雖於教中未有文作然依<a 
name="0723b05" id="0723b05"></a>道理義合須然故依理施羯磨成立以成立故名為<a 
name="0723b06" id="0723b06"></a>良慧餘思可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復有五種至非法羯磨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0723b07" id="0723b07"></a>明五偽文分三分謂標列釋釋中有五一偽制學處二<a 
name="0723b08" id="0723b08"></a>偽制所犯三偽制出離四偽制止息五偽制羯磨一一<a 
name="0723b09" id="0723b09"></a>事別如文可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次除十至非清淨說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十二<a 
name="0723b10" id="0723b10"></a>非淨宣說門文分三分一摽二徵三釋非淨此初也。</p><a 
name="0723b11" id="0723b11"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何十事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二徵數也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論一於佛寶至不清<a 
name="0723b12" id="0723b12"></a>淨事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三釋分二先明淨說後不淨說初中有<a 
name="0723b13" id="0723b13"></a>十一欲<span class="gaiji">損<!--gaiji,損,1[損-口+ㄙ],2,3--></span>等除斯十種清淨說外餘名不淨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若因<a 
name="0724a01" id="0724a01"></a>嫉姤至不清淨說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後不淨說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次毗奈至<a 
name="0724a02" id="0724a02"></a>譬喻事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰十三譬喻顯法門文分為二初&#x60E3;摽<a 
name="0724a03" id="0724a03"></a>列後別解釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論本生事者至菩薩行事。</p><a 
name="0724a04" id="0724a04"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別釋中文分為五一辯本生二明本事三彰<a 
name="0724a05" id="0724a05"></a>影像四明假合五彰譬喻初本生者如佛自說前所<a 
name="0724a06" id="0724a06"></a>經事名曰本生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論本事事者至相應事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明<a 
name="0724a07" id="0724a07"></a>本事謂說前世三乘弟子於教行中相應事也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0724a08" id="0724a08"></a>影像事者至應了知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰影像文中有二先<a 
name="0724a09" id="0724a09"></a>五後七影依質起而似質者顯相似義以影像等顯<a 
name="0724a10" id="0724a10"></a>所似法而有五種謂乳等五種喻於聲聞緣覺小<a 
name="0724a11" id="0724a11"></a>大菩薩及如來也後七人者如涅槃經三十六說恒河<a 
name="0724a12" id="0724a12"></a>七人也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論假合事者至合而說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明假合以彼<a 
name="0724a13" id="0724a13"></a>說此名為假合如經頌云第六王為最第六意識實非<a 
name="0724a14" id="0724a14"></a>是王由多自在故名王也餘准此知良醫喻者如經說<a 
name="0724b01" id="0724b01"></a>佛名大醫王佛實非醫以能了知根法藥病故名為<a 
name="0724b02" id="0724b02"></a>醫餘可知矣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論譬喻事者至如是等類。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五彰<a 
name="0724b03" id="0724b03"></a>譬喻如說火宅事理廣長名廣等喻餘思可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0724b04" id="0724b04"></a>復次由五至差別故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第三所知法異門文分三<a 
name="0724b05" id="0724b05"></a>分一慧知心境分二識所了別分三獲得勝利分初<a 
name="0724b06" id="0724b06"></a>中有四一摽二徵三列四釋此初三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何由事至所<a 
name="0724b07" id="0724b07"></a>知事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋文中分為五一明體事二彰品業三辯<a 
name="0724b08" id="0724b08"></a>智依四明智別五辯攝餘初中文二謂徵及釋所知體<a 
name="0724b09" id="0724b09"></a>事不出有為及無為也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何由品至所知作業。</p><a 
name="0724b10" id="0724b10"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰品業文分為四一摽二徵三釋四結此初摽<a 
name="0724b11" id="0724b11"></a>中徵及荅也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論何等為五至名所知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二徵三<a 
name="0724b12" id="0724b12"></a>釋釋中有二一辯所知二明作業初中有五如文可知。</p><a 
name="0724b13" id="0724b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若世俗智至而起眾行。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明作業謂諸聖<a 
name="0725a01" id="0725a01"></a>智而能有彼五所知用名五作業一明俗智知初所知<a 
name="0725a02" id="0725a02"></a>文別有二一了世道理二了世言行了世理中不善有罪<a 
name="0725a03" id="0725a03"></a>善無罪法如次遠離應脩習也了世言中了世言說詮<a 
name="0725a04" id="0725a04"></a>真不迨但隨世轉名遊世間因世名言而有所作名<a 
name="0725a05" id="0725a05"></a>隨因緣起諸眾行。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論法智類智至法斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明<a 
name="0725a06" id="0725a06"></a>真智知勝義境文分為二初明六智知其真境後例見<a 
name="0725a07" id="0725a07"></a>修斷所斷智六智之中初二為&#x60E3;後四為別&#x60E3;別合論<a 
name="0725a08" id="0725a08"></a>故為六也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論盡智至離增上<span class="gaiji">慢<!--gaiji,慢,1[慢-又+方],2&#x22894;,3--></span>。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰二智知無<a 
name="0725a09" id="0725a09"></a>學果無學果體名為究竟於中文二先釋所知後彰知<a 
name="0725a10" id="0725a10"></a>意。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論他心智至界及隨眠。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明心智能了他心界<a 
name="0725a11" id="0725a11"></a>者性也隨眠種子謂他心智能知眾生染淨心性意<a 
name="0725a12" id="0725a12"></a>樂不同復能了知心性種子發生差別以上勝智心性<a 
name="0725a13" id="0725a13"></a>現種皆能知故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論十力智至及安樂事。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五明<a 
name="0725a14" id="0725a14"></a>力智能知種別具本地分問所知之境豈只五耶荅五<a 
name="0725b01" id="0725b01"></a>攝之盡若尒何有非安立耶荅勝義智中<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>攝之故<a 
name="0725b02" id="0725b02"></a>若尒初二攝所知盡何假後三再言重設荅對能知智<a 
name="0725b03" id="0725b03"></a>用有差別故說之也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是名為至五種業。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四<a 
name="0725b04" id="0725b04"></a>&#x60E3;結也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何由智至依處差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三辯智依<a 
name="0725b05" id="0725b05"></a>文分為二先徵後釋釋中有四摽列釋結釋中有<a 
name="0725b06" id="0725b06"></a>二初明自行後明他行與前五業十智相攝如文可知。</p><a 
name="0725b07" id="0725b07"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何由智至唯世間。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明智別顯前十智及<a 
name="0725b08" id="0725b08"></a>十力智是世出世漏無漏別文分為五一明俗智俗<a 
name="0725b09" id="0725b09"></a>智有二一有漏三性是世間故名為俗智二在無學身<a 
name="0725b10" id="0725b10"></a>善無記性無漏所起雖名無漏體是漏故亦名俗智<a 
name="0725b11" id="0725b11"></a>及所餘者及餘有學異生所起皆俗智也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論當知所<a 
name="0725b12" id="0725b12"></a>餘至亦喻無漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明真智心境無漏名出世間<a 
name="0725b13" id="0725b13"></a>體即法類六種智也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論盡無生智至相續中生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0726a01" id="0726a01"></a>曰三盡無生體唯無漏通世出世若不分別緣理而起名<a 
name="0726a02" id="0726a02"></a>為出世若起分別緣事生故名曰世間由未曾得在無<a 
name="0726a03" id="0726a03"></a>學身故名出世及無漏故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論他心智至是無漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0726a04" id="0726a04"></a>曰四他心智文分為二初正分別後明無漏此初也無<a 
name="0726a05" id="0726a05"></a>學所得雖通無漏以緣事故唯是世間非證理心不<a 
name="0726a06" id="0726a06"></a>名出世。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問何因緣故至名無漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明無漏文<a 
name="0726a07" id="0726a07"></a>分為二先問後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至皆成無漏。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0726a08" id="0726a08"></a>後荅文二先釋後結是故<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>下結由三義故成無漏。</p><a 
name="0726a09" id="0726a09"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論十力智至而現行故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五十力智唯是世間何<a 
name="0726a10" id="0726a10"></a>以然者謂由此智皆帶名言戲論生故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何由<a 
name="0726a11" id="0726a11"></a>攝至諸智所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五辯攝餘文分三分一明十智<a 
name="0726a12" id="0726a12"></a>攝通空門二重分別通諍願智三明通智生得時異<a 
name="0726a13" id="0726a13"></a>初中有二先徵後釋釋中又二初摽後攝此初摽舉<a 
name="0726a14" id="0726a14"></a>神通等智皆是如前十智所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂五神通至如<a 
name="0726b01" id="0726b01"></a>前應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後攝之中文分三分初攝六通次攝<a 
name="0726b02" id="0726b02"></a>空門後攝無礙初中有二一攝前五二攝第六謂前五<a 
name="0726b03" id="0726b03"></a>通皆是前說十智之中初俗智攝其中凡夫及有學<a 
name="0726b04" id="0726b04"></a>者五通皆漏無學得者即唯無漏第六漏盡唯是無<a 
name="0726b05" id="0726b05"></a>學故是盡智無生智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論空解脫門至無生智。</p><a 
name="0726b06" id="0726b06"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次攝空門文分三分初辯空門次明無願後彰<a 
name="0726b07" id="0726b07"></a>無相初空門中但攝八智不攝俗及他心者此二緣<a 
name="0726b08" id="0726b08"></a>有故不攝空&#x63D4;空無我遍緣四諦故四諦智得攝空<a 
name="0726b09" id="0726b09"></a>門次無願中但攝六智非滅等者滅道無漏非無願<a 
name="0726b10" id="0726b10"></a>也俗智他心是意所求亦非無願故但攝六而無增<a 
name="0726b11" id="0726b11"></a>也後無相中但攝五智不攝道者道雖無漏而相非<a 
name="0726b12" id="0726b12"></a>無故無相門唯五智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論無礙解智至盡當知。</p><a 
name="0726b13" id="0726b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後攝無礙不共等智以緣俗故故皆俗攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論<a 
name="0726b14" id="0726b14"></a>諸解脫門至地<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二重分別通諍願智文<a 
name="0727a01" id="0727a01"></a>分為二先指後釋此初也三解脫門如本地分二十<a 
name="0727a02" id="0727a02"></a>六明四無礙解如菩薩地四十五辯十力無量不共<a 
name="0727a03" id="0727a03"></a>佛法如四十九及五十說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云何至智作證。</p><a 
name="0727a04" id="0727a04"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋之中文分為二一別釋神通無諍願智二<a 
name="0727a05" id="0727a05"></a>&#x63D4;明無諍願通定別初中有三一辯神通二明無諍<a 
name="0727a06" id="0727a06"></a>三明願智初辯神通文復有二一別辯六通二&#x63D4;明<a 
name="0727a07" id="0727a07"></a>具用初中分六一明神境二明天耳三辯他心四明<a 
name="0727a08" id="0727a08"></a>宿住五明死生六明漏盡初神境中文分三分先徵<a 
name="0727a09" id="0727a09"></a>次釋後&#x63D4;結之此初牒經而問三事一所變境二能<a 
name="0727a10" id="0727a10"></a>變智三作證名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂從一種至名為神境。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0727a11" id="0727a11"></a>次釋如徵亦分三段初明神境次彰神智後釋證名<a 
name="0727a12" id="0727a12"></a>初神境中文復有二一明境體二辯名因所變境中<a 
name="0727a13" id="0727a13"></a>而有二種一變二化變謂改易變一為多小為大等<a 
name="0727a14" id="0727a14"></a>改易舊質目之為變無而忽有稱之為化言至梵世<a 
name="0727b01" id="0727b01"></a>自在轉等通其變化二由神境下顯得名因所變化<a 
name="0727b02" id="0727b02"></a>境而非是神由神現之故名神境神體謂即智慧者也正<a 
name="0727b03" id="0727b03"></a>理雖說通定及慧此及有宗即唯智也以智用勝餘<a 
name="0727b04" id="0727b04"></a>莫能測故謂為神。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若智至名神境智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次<a 
name="0727b05" id="0727b05"></a>彰神智文分為二一明智體二釋神名神通之體謂<a 
name="0727b06" id="0727b06"></a>即智也智能變化少多自在名具威德因定所發名<a 
name="0727b07" id="0727b07"></a>為修果由此智下辯得名因智非其境為能領納及<a 
name="0727b08" id="0727b08"></a>能顯示故得境名依主釋也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論即此智種至智作<a 
name="0727b09" id="0727b09"></a>證。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋證名眾生無始數得神通皆有種子<a 
name="0727b10" id="0727b10"></a>由性事障不能起用今明行者由離二障修習勢力<a 
name="0727b11" id="0727b11"></a>令舊種子增長相續尒時緣具得起神通故言此種<a 
name="0727b12" id="0727b12"></a>由生緣等即親種子&#x8E08;緣助故而能起現名為作證<a 
name="0727b13" id="0727b13"></a>作猶起也種能生起證得通智名作證也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是<a 
name="0727b14" id="0727b14"></a>一切至作證通。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後&#x63D4;結也如是一切境智及<a 
name="0728a01" id="0728a01"></a>證&#x63D4;攝名一神境智通。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何天耳至如前說。</p><a 
name="0728a02" id="0728a02"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明天耳文分三分謂徵釋結釋中有三一明<a 
name="0728a03" id="0728a03"></a>修果謂天耳根因定起也二天耳智與天耳識俱時<a 
name="0728a04" id="0728a04"></a>智也三智作證耳智種也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次由此至今當說。</p><a 
name="0728a05" id="0728a05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三辯他心文分為二初&#x63D4;摽指後別釋之此指<a 
name="0728a06" id="0728a06"></a>問詞同前不舉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂諸他心至如前說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0728a07" id="0728a07"></a>別釋中文分為二先釋後結釋中有三一明差別彰<a 
name="0728a08" id="0728a08"></a>所緣境二明修果辯能緣智三明作證因修種生結<a 
name="0728a09" id="0728a09"></a>文可悉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若於過去至如前說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明宿住<a 
name="0728a10" id="0728a10"></a>文分三段若過去下明所緣境若智具下辯能緣智<a 
name="0728a11" id="0728a11"></a>餘如前說指作證等智隨念起名隨念智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若諸<a 
name="0728a12" id="0728a12"></a>有情至如前說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五明死生文亦有三若有情<a 
name="0728a13" id="0728a13"></a>下明所緣境若修果下辯能緣智餘如前說指作證<a 
name="0728a14" id="0728a14"></a>等問緣死生通是何識智荅眼意二識相應智也意<a 
name="0728b01" id="0728b01"></a>相應智也意緣死生理極成就意識必由天眼為依故<a 
name="0728b02" id="0728b02"></a>名天眼非唯眼識名天眼也未自在位眼識不緣未<a 
name="0728b03" id="0728b03"></a>來境故若眼識慧如何得緣未來境耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若一切結<a 
name="0728b04" id="0728b04"></a>至如前應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰六明漏盡准問有三云何漏盡云<a 
name="0728b05" id="0728b05"></a>何通智云何作證而今荅文亦有三也一切結盡荅<a 
name="0728b06" id="0728b06"></a>初問盡無生智荅第二問餘一切下荅第三問盡無生<a 
name="0728b07" id="0728b07"></a>智雖通真俗今取了世故名通智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次諸具至神<a 
name="0728b08" id="0728b08"></a>通者。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二&#x60E3;明具用文分三段一辯具通二彰勝劣<a 
name="0728b09" id="0728b09"></a>三明利用此初辯中義別分四一示現者神境通也<a 
name="0728b10" id="0728b10"></a>示現神通起化物故二安住者天耳他心二種通也雖聞語<a 
name="0728b11" id="0728b11"></a>聲及知心<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>未行施化而自審思名為安住或安有<a 
name="0728b12" id="0728b12"></a>情各住自行名為安住三他利者宿住死生謂知所<a 
name="0728b13" id="0728b13"></a>化過未善惡令起斷修名利他也四問記者漏盡通<a 
name="0729a01" id="0729a01"></a>也由漏盡故故善問記。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次前三至三世愚故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演<a 
name="0729a02" id="0729a02"></a>曰二彰勝劣前三現在通而非明後三種通亦兼明攝<a 
name="0729a03" id="0729a03"></a>何以然者以宿住等如次能治過未現在三世愚闇故<a 
name="0729a04" id="0729a04"></a>得明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又初神通至能善教授。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三彰利用文<a 
name="0729a05" id="0729a05"></a>中有二初辯前三後辯後三後三之中離常等者由<a 
name="0729a06" id="0729a06"></a>得宿住示生過去因果相生常見因遣由死生智示生<a 
name="0729a07" id="0729a07"></a>未來生處差別便除斷見謂由漏盡於現在中宣說<a 
name="0729a08" id="0729a08"></a>中道故通雖同用各差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次觀察至住&#x65E0;諍<a 
name="0729a09" id="0729a09"></a>定。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明無諍文分三&#x53DA;一辯住定因二明無諍行<a 
name="0729a10" id="0729a10"></a>三結無諍名初中有二先摽後釋釋中有三一聞昔勝<a 
name="0729a11" id="0729a11"></a>利而修無諍二悔昔諍心修無諍行三令受愛果修<a 
name="0729a12" id="0729a12"></a>無諍定此等皆是利根無學方行此行揀鈍不然名<a 
name="0729a13" id="0729a13"></a>俱解脫須菩提等即其人也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論由此因緣至如是勸<a 
name="0729a14" id="0729a14"></a>導。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明無諍行文分為二一此因緣下辯定釋<a 
name="0729b01" id="0729b01"></a>名二如是為下辯無諍行無諍行中文復有二一明見<a 
name="0729b02" id="0729b02"></a>不見二明語不語。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論彼由多分至無諍者。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三結<a 
name="0729b03" id="0729b03"></a>無諍名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何願智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明願智文分為二先問<a 
name="0729b04" id="0729b04"></a>後荅此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂俱分解脫至依止故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅<a 
name="0729b05" id="0729b05"></a>文二先辯二乘後明佛願初中有三一辯起願人二彰<a 
name="0729b06" id="0729b06"></a>所依定三辯修願相此初二也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若聲聞乘至一切了<a 
name="0729b07" id="0729b07"></a>知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三辯修願相文有其二一顯修相二既入下明<a 
name="0729b08" id="0729b08"></a>願成就并顯其名。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若諸如來至無障礙。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0729b09" id="0729b09"></a>後明佛願。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次諸佛至不能棄捨。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二&#x60E3;明<a 
name="0729b10" id="0729b10"></a>無諍願通定別文分為二一明無諍入有差別二明無<a 
name="0729b11" id="0729b11"></a>諍願通定異此初有三摽徵及釋此無諍定小乘數入<a 
name="0729b12" id="0729b12"></a>大乘不數何以然者以利他時因起諍心而得脫故故<a 
name="0729b13" id="0729b13"></a>不數入。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次如熏至皆能引發。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明無諍願<a 
name="0730a01" id="0730a01"></a>通定異文分為二一者正明依定多少二者因明人觀地<a 
name="0730a02" id="0730a02"></a>別此初也謂無諍等行微細故唯依第四神通行<span class="gaiji">麤<!--gaiji,麤,1[夕/鹿],2,3--></span>故<a 
name="0730a03" id="0730a03"></a>通四定。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次唯依至聖諦現觀。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明入觀文<a 
name="0730a04" id="0730a04"></a>分為二初辯依心後辯生身此初分三標徵及釋謂依<a 
name="0730a05" id="0730a05"></a>五地慧心勝故能入現觀無色不然故不依入。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論非生<a 
name="0730a06" id="0730a06"></a>上地至少分亦無。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯生身依生欲界猒心勝故<a 
name="0730a07" id="0730a07"></a>能入現觀上界不然故不依入故顯揚頌云極慼非惡<a 
name="0730a08" id="0730a08"></a>趣極忻非上二處欲界人天佛出世現觀。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次當<a 
name="0730a09" id="0730a09"></a>說至生起差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明通智生得時異文分為二<a 
name="0730a10" id="0730a10"></a>一辯智生二明通得初中有二先摽後釋此初摽舉<a 
name="0730a11" id="0730a11"></a>世出世智三際生別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂世俗智至應知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後<a 
name="0730a12" id="0730a12"></a>釋文二一明世俗二明出世初中有二一辯二乘二明菩<a 
name="0730a13" id="0730a13"></a>薩二乘有三一明前際二明中際三彰後際前際分<a 
name="0730a14" id="0730a14"></a>二先釋後結釋中又二先辯所治後辯能治此辯所<a 
name="0730b01" id="0730b01"></a>治染心也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論為欲生起至世俗智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯能<a 
name="0730b02" id="0730b02"></a>治文分三段一起善法攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論以此正見至世俗智攝。</p><a 
name="0730b03" id="0730b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二具正資&#x7CAE;聞思二心於念住等勤修行者亦<a 
name="0730b04" id="0730b04"></a>俗智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論以此為依至世俗智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三修順&#x51B3;<a 
name="0730b05" id="0730b05"></a>擇文分為三初明燸頂次明忍位後世第一此初二位<a 
name="0730b06" id="0730b06"></a>名方便者而是見道遠方便也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論以此為依至世俗<a 
name="0730b07" id="0730b07"></a>智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次明忍位漸近見道近方便也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論以此<a 
name="0730b08" id="0730b08"></a>為依至世俗智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後世第一雖一<span class="gaiji">剎<!--gaiji,剎,1[利-禾+(ㄆ/小)],2&#x206F4;,3--></span>那引生見<a 
name="0730b09" id="0730b09"></a>道亦是有漏世俗智攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是名為至生起次第。</p><a 
name="0730b10" id="0730b10"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後&#x60E3;結也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又即以彼至諸世俗智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明<a 
name="0730b11" id="0730b11"></a>中際文別有二先釋後結釋中又二一正彰智體二明<a 
name="0730b12" id="0730b12"></a>地有無初中復二一明智體用二彰修智道初文分二<a 
name="0730b13" id="0730b13"></a>先明體用後釋異名初文又二一明種體二明起用初<a 
name="0731a01" id="0731a01"></a>智體中文復分三謂摽釋結得清淨者謂前二位<a 
name="0731a02" id="0731a02"></a>世俗智種由得見道斷染法故名得清淨彼資熏故<a 
name="0731a03" id="0731a03"></a>亦&#x53F7;為修對法十三亦具明也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論出見道<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>至非謂<a 
name="0731a04" id="0731a04"></a>永斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明起用文別有六一證見斷下自了證得<a 
name="0731a05" id="0731a05"></a>擇非擇滅二又能了下自知得果三又能了下自知所<a 
name="0731a06" id="0731a06"></a>斷惑之差別四又隨欲下能善記別五又能於下能建<a 
name="0731a07" id="0731a07"></a>諦觀六復於此下能伏煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>伏煩<span class="gaiji">惱<!--gaiji,惱,1[惱-囟+山],2&#x22649;,3--></span>中文復分二一明<a 
name="0731a08" id="0731a08"></a>能伏二明伏法此所得智唯是有漏故唯伏惑若無<a 
name="0731a09" id="0731a09"></a>漏者亦能斷彼迷事隨眠此彰俗智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此世俗智<a 
name="0731a10" id="0731a10"></a>至為世間。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二釋異名雖體有漏由從無漏智後<a 
name="0731a11" id="0731a11"></a>引生不同異生故不一向名世閒也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又修此智至勝進<a 
name="0731a12" id="0731a12"></a>道。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二彰修智道文分為二初&#x63D4;摽列後別解釋<a 
name="0731a13" id="0731a13"></a>此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於一切地至第三道。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別解中文分<a 
name="0731a14" id="0731a14"></a>為四一明方便二明無閒三明解脫四明勝進此前三<a 
name="0731b01" id="0731b01"></a>也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論次後於斷是第四道。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明勝進文分為<a 
name="0731b02" id="0731b02"></a>二先&#x60E3;略釋後別分別此初也後後品道而勝前前名<a 
name="0731b03" id="0731b03"></a>為勝進。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論此勝進道至名勝進。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別分別文<a 
name="0731b04" id="0731b04"></a>復分二先標後釋釋中有二一方便勝進二知足勝進。</p><a 
name="0731b05" id="0731b05"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論除未至定至所攝受故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明地有無文分三<a 
name="0731b06" id="0731b06"></a>&#x53DA;一明上七地近分唯俗二辯八根本及初未至唯真<a 
name="0731b07" id="0731b07"></a>非俗三明上有頂唯俗非真根本地中雖通真俗聖所<a 
name="0731b08" id="0731b08"></a>修者即唯真故今明俗智故以揀之。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論始從學地至<a 
name="0731b09" id="0731b09"></a>中際俗智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後&#x60E3;結也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於阿羅漢至俗智攝。</p><a 
name="0731b10" id="0731b10"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明後際文分為二先釋後結義思可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復<a 
name="0731b11" id="0731b11"></a>次諸菩薩至世俗智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明菩薩三際俗智文分<a 
name="0731b12" id="0731b12"></a>為二先&#x60E3;摽舉後各別釋此初也到究竟者第十地中<a 
name="0731b13" id="0731b13"></a>因滿究竟非彰佛位說為究竟。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論初際者至究竟<a 
name="0732a01" id="0732a01"></a>地。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別釋中文分為二初彰三際後明三行此<a 
name="0732a02" id="0732a02"></a>明三際俗智差別約位明體故名地等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又諸菩薩<a 
name="0732a03" id="0732a03"></a>至則不如是。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明三行對彰勝劣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次如是<a 
name="0732a04" id="0732a04"></a>至我當說。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明出世文分三&#x53DA;初結前生後次<a 
name="0732a05" id="0732a05"></a>依生正釋後&#x60E3;結之此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論謂見道修道無學道。</p><a 
name="0732a06" id="0732a06"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次依生正釋文分為二初列後辯此初摽列出世<a 
name="0732a07" id="0732a07"></a>三道。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若法智品至見所斷惑。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後辯分三先<a 
name="0732a08" id="0732a08"></a>明見道次明修道後無學道初中有二先明見體後<a 
name="0732a09" id="0732a09"></a>別分別此初先明八法八類以為見體倣法擬&#x519D;說<a 
name="0732a10" id="0732a10"></a>之為斷。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論問一切類智至無色界耶。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後別分別<a 
name="0732a11" id="0732a11"></a>文分三&#x53DA;初彰了境次明相攝後明增長初具問荅<a 
name="0732a12" id="0732a12"></a>此先問也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論荅至不能了別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後荅可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論所<a 
name="0732a13" id="0732a13"></a>餘諸智至二品所攝。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次明相攝止觀俱智隨彼<a 
name="0732a14" id="0732a14"></a>法類二智所攝故無增減。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又於見道至勝進道。</p><a 
name="0732b01" id="0732b01"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後明增長餘智因者後智種也十六心中初智生<a 
name="0732b02" id="0732b02"></a>時餘十五智親生種別皆得增長以增長故說為得<a 
name="0732b03" id="0732b03"></a>修因得修故而漸生長故名勝進。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論於修道中至出<a 
name="0732b04" id="0732b04"></a>世智。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰次明修道文分為二一&#x60E3;明修習世出世道<a 
name="0732b05" id="0732b05"></a>二別釋修習世道所以此修二道如文可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論為於<a 
name="0732b06" id="0732b06"></a>諸諦至而離諸欲演曰二別釋修習世道所以文分<a 
name="0732b07" id="0732b07"></a>為二先釋後結釋中有四四箇故字是釋世道修習<a 
name="0732b08" id="0732b08"></a>所以論無學地中至皆自在轉。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後無學道文<a 
name="0732b09" id="0732b09"></a>中有二一斷惑清淨二為德依持。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是名為至次<a 
name="0732b10" id="0732b10"></a>第生起。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後&#x60E3;結也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次諸神境智至或生<a 
name="0732b11" id="0732b11"></a>得。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明通得文分為二一明神境二辯餘通初中<a 
name="0732b12" id="0732b12"></a>有二先摽後釋此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論方便得者至所有修果。</p><a 
name="0732b13" id="0732b13"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後釋分二一明方便二明生得此方便也如有生<a 
name="0733a01" id="0733a01"></a>此欲界異生及有學等修得通者名方便得揀生上界<a 
name="0733a02" id="0733a02"></a>不名方便&#x5C5E;生得故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論生得者至起屍等。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二<a 
name="0733a03" id="0733a03"></a>明生得類別分六一色界天二欲界天三欲界人四有<a 
name="0733a04" id="0733a04"></a>傍生五分鬼趣六&#x546A;術得&#x546A;術得者依生所起亦名<a 
name="0733a05" id="0733a05"></a>生得言<span class="gaiji">曼<!--gaiji,曼,1[曼-又+万],2&#x3B05;,3--></span><span class="gaiji">馱<!--gaiji,馱,1[馬*犬],2&#x4B7E;,3--></span>多者此云持養或云我能即頂生王也<a 
name="0733a06" id="0733a06"></a>頂生王父於祖膊生名膊生王膊生王頂時有胞出後時<a 
name="0733a07" id="0733a07"></a>自裂中有一童儼如化出膊生大王謂諸夫人誰能持養<a 
name="0733a08" id="0733a08"></a>皆言我能時王因付第一夫人因立其名名為持養<a 
name="0733a09" id="0733a09"></a>言頂生者而從生處以立其名非正翻也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論即由如<a 
name="0733a10" id="0733a10"></a>是至當知亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二辯餘通除神境外餘天眼耳<a 
name="0733a11" id="0733a11"></a>宿住他心修得生得一同神境名為亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次云<a 
name="0733a12" id="0733a12"></a>何至生差別故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰第二識所了別分文分為二<a 
name="0733a13" id="0733a13"></a>先徵後釋釋中有四一摽二徵三列四釋此前三也。</p><a 
name="0733a14" id="0733a14"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何依緣至以為境界。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四釋分五一辯依緣二<a 
name="0733b01" id="0733b01"></a>明欣慼三明勝劣四明心法五障治生初中有二先徵<a 
name="0733b02" id="0733b02"></a>後釋。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何欣慼至非二諸法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明欣慼。</p><a 
name="0733b03" id="0733b03"></a><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何勝劣至自所行法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明勝劣。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何<a 
name="0733b04" id="0733b04"></a>心法至一切境法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四明心法先徵後辯辯中<a 
name="0733b05" id="0733b05"></a>有二先摽後釋釋中又二先辨遍心後善心所善心所<a 
name="0733b06" id="0733b06"></a>中文復有二初明增減後彰假實。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論云何障治至<a 
name="0733b07" id="0733b07"></a>自所行法。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五障治生文分二分一徵二釋釋中<a 
name="0733b08" id="0733b08"></a>又三一明障別二明治別三明生別此初二中文復分<a 
name="0733b09" id="0733b09"></a>三一辯所治二辯能治三明治識披之可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論復次<a 
name="0733b10" id="0733b10"></a>生差別者至自地二心。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰三明生別文分為四一<a 
name="0733b11" id="0733b11"></a>摽二列三釋四結釋中有五一明欲生二明色生三無<a 
name="0733b12" id="0733b12"></a>色生四&#x5F83;上生五還下生此前三也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若先未起至<a 
name="0733b13" id="0733b13"></a>無學心生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四&#x5F83;上生文分為二一明修定二明生<a 
name="0734a01" id="0734a01"></a>上初中有二一辯善心二明無記初中又二先釋後例<a 
name="0734a02" id="0734a02"></a>釋中有二一明次第二明超越此初復二一起上心二<a 
name="0734a03" id="0734a03"></a>起學心披可知也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論若先<span class="corr" title='[巳&gt;已]'>已</span>起至如意能起。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰<a 
name="0734a04" id="0734a04"></a>二明超越初久修別故分二種。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是所餘至當知<a 
name="0734a05" id="0734a05"></a>亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰後例初禪起餘上心次第超越一同於初<a 
name="0734a06" id="0734a06"></a>名為亦尒。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又從欲界至非自性故。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明無<a 
name="0734a07" id="0734a07"></a>記無記無間能生上地思准可知。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又欲界沒至<a 
name="0734a08" id="0734a08"></a>生起差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明生上了生差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又諸異生<a 
name="0734a09" id="0734a09"></a>至無間生。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰五辯還下生文分為二先起下心後<a 
name="0734a10" id="0734a10"></a>明生下此初也。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論又從上地至生起差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰二明<a 
name="0734a11" id="0734a11"></a>生下。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 0em"><span class="linehead"></span>論如是障治至諸法差別。</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-left: 1em"><span class="linehead"></span>演曰四&#x60E3;結也。</p><a 
name="0734a12" id="0734a12"></a><a 
name="0734a13" id="0734a13"></a><p><span class="juanname">瑜伽師地論義演卷第二十八</span></p>
